hadiths[257]{hadithnumber,text}:
5970,"hamein us ghar waley ne khabar di aur unhon-ne apne hath se Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ki taraf ishara kya, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha Allah Taala ke nazdeek kon sa amal sabse zyada pasand hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke waqt par Namaz padhna . puchha ke phir kon sa ? farmaya ke waalidain ke sath achchha sulook karnaa, puchha phir kon sa ? farmaya ke Allah ke rastey mein jihad karna. Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se un kaamon ke mutaalliq bayan kya aur agar main isi tarah sawal karta rehta to aap jawab detey rehtey."
5971,"aik sahabi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! mere achchhey sulook ka sabse zyada haqdaar kon hai? farmaya ke tumhari maan hai. puchha iske baad kon hai? farmaya ke tumhari maan hai. unhon-ne phir puchha iske baad kaun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhari maan hai. unhon-ne puchha iske baad kon hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tumhara bap hai. ibne- shabarma aur Yahya bin Ayub ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Abu-Zaraa ne usi ke mutabiq bayan kya."
5972,aik sahabi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha kya main bhi jihad mein Sharik ho jaaun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey maan-baap maujood hain unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan maujood hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir unhiin mein jihad karo.
5973,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yaqinan sabse badey gunahon mein se ye hai ke koi shakhs apne waalidain par laanat bhejey. puchha gaya : ya Rasulullah! koi shakhs apne hi waalidain par kaisey laanat bhejega? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo shakhs doosrey ke bap ko bura-bhala kahega to doosra bhi iske bap ko aur uski maan ko bura-bhala kahega.
5974,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke teen aadmi chal rahe they ke barish ne unhein aa liya aur unhon-ne mud kar pahaadii ki ghaar mein panah li. iske baad unke ghaar ke munh par pahaad ki aik chattaan giri aur uska munh band ho gaya. ab ek ne doosrey se kaha ke tum ne jo nek kaam kiye hain unmein se aisey kaam ko dhyaan mein lao jo tum ne khalis Allah ke liye kya ho taake Allah se iske zariey dua karo mumkin hai wo ghaar ko khol de. is par unmein se aik ne kaha : aey Allah ! mere waalidain they aur bahut boodhey they aur mere chhotey chhotey bachchey bhi they. main unke liye bakriyan charaataa tha aur wapas aa kar doodh nikaaltaa to sabse pahley apne waalidain ko pilaataa tha apne bachchon se bhi pahley. aik din chaarey ki talash ne mujhey bahut door ley ja daala chunanche main raat gaey wapas aaya. maine dekha ke mere waalidain so chukey hain. maine mamool (routine) ke mutabiq doodh nikala phir main dohaa hua doodh lekar aaya aur unke sarhaaney khada ho gaya mein gawara nahi kar sakta tha ke unhein soney mein jagaaoon aur ye bhi mujh se nahi ho sakta tha ke waalidain se pahley bachchon ko pilaaun. bachchey bhook se mere qadmon par lait rahe they aur usi kash-m-kash mein subah ho gaee. to aey Allah ! agar terey ilm mein bhi ye kaam maine sirf teri raza hasil karne ke liye kya tha to hamarey liye kushadgi paida kar de ke ham aasman dekh sakein. Allah Taala ne (dua'a qabool ki aur) unke liye itni kushadgi paida kar di ke wo aasman dekh saktey they. doosrey shakhs ne kaha : aey Allaah! meri aik chacha zaad behan thi aur main us se mohabbat karta tha, wo intihai mohabbat jo aik mard aik aurat se kar sakta hai. maine us se usey maanga to usne inkar kya aur sirf is shart par razi hui ke main usey so Dinar dun. maine daud-dhoop ki aur so Dinar jama kar laya phir uske paas unhein lekar gaya phir jab main iske donon paon ke darmyan mein baith gaya to usne kaha ke aey Allah ke bandey! Allah se dar aur mehar ko mat tod. main ye sun kar khada ho gaya (aur zina se baaz raha) to agar terey ilm mein bhi maine ye kaam teri raza w khushnoodii hasil karne ke liye kya tha to hamarey liye kuchh aur kushadgi (chattaan ko hata kar) paida kar de. chunanche unke liye thodi si aur kushadgi ho gaii. teesrey shakhs ne kaha : aey Allaah! maine aik mazdoor aik farq chaawal ki mazdoorii par rakha tha us ne apna kaam pura karke kaha ke meri mazdoorii do. maine uski mazdoorii de di lekin wo chhod kar chala gaya aur uske sath be-tawajjohi ki. mein uske us bachey huey dhaan ko botaa raha aur is tarah maine us se aik gaaey aur iska charwaha kar liya (phir jab wo aaya to) maine us se kaha ke ye gaaey aur charwaha ley jao. usne kaha Allah se daro aur mere sath mazaaq na karo. maine kaha ke main tumharey sath mazaaq nahi karta. us gaaey aur charwaahey ko ley jao. chunanche wo unhein lekar chala gaya. to agar terey ilm mein bhi maine ye kaam teri raza w khushnoodii hasil karne ke liye kya tha to (chattaan ki wjah se ghaar se nikalney mein jo rukawat baqi reh gaee hai usey bhi khol de. chunanche Allah Taala ne unke liye poori tarah kushadgi kar di jis se wo bahar aa gaey."
5975,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ne tum par maa ki nafarmani haram qarar di hai aur) waalidain ke huquq ( na dena aur nahaq unse mataalbaat (maangein) karna bhi haram qarar diya hai, ladkiyon ko zinda dafn karna ( bhi haram qarar diya hai) aur) قيل وقال ( (fuzool baatein) kasarate-sawaal aur maal ki barbadi ko bhi na-pasand kya hai."
5976,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen sabse bada gunah na bataaun ? ham ne arz kya zaroor bataiye ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke sath shirk karna aur waalidain ki nafarmani karna. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt tek lagaey huey they ab aap seedhey baith gaey aur farmaya aagah ho jao jhooti baat bhi aur jhooti gawahi bhi (sab se badey gunah hain) aagah ho jao jhooti baat bhi aur jhooti gawahi bhii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey musalsal dohraatey rahe aur maine sochaa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh nahi hongey.
5977,"mujh se Ubaidullaah-bin-abii-Bakar ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badey gunah ka zikr kya ya (unhon-ne kaha ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se badey gunahon ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke sath shirk karnaa, kisi ki (naahaq) jaan lena , waalidain ki nafarmani karna phir farmaya kya main tumhen sabse bada gunah na bata dun? farmaya ke jhooti baat ya farmaya ke jhooti shahadat (sab se bada gunah hai) Shoba ne bayan kya ke mera ghalib guman ye hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jhooti gawahi farmaya tha."
5978,"meri walida Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein mere paas aaein, wo Islam se munkar thin. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha kya main iske sath sila rehmii kar sakti hon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan. iske baad Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki (لا ينهاكم الله an (an) الذين لم يقاتلوكم في الدين) yaanii ''Allah paak tum ko un logon ke sath nek sulook karne se mana nahi karta jo tum se hamarey Deen ke mutaalliq koi ladai jhagdaa nahi kartey.''"
5979,"meri walida mushrika thin wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Quraish ke sath suleh ke zamane main apne walid ke sath (Madina Munawra ( aaein . maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unke mutaalliq puchha ke meri walida aai hain aur wo Islam se alag hain (kya mein unke sath sila rehmii kar sakti hon?) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, apni walida ke sath sila rehmii karo."
5980,"Hiraql ne unhein bula bheja to unhon-ne usey bataya ke wo yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein namaaz, sadqa, paak daamanii aur sila rehmii ka hukm farmatey hain."
5981,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne سیراء ka (eik reshamii ( hulla biktey dekha to arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap usey khareed lein aur Juma ke din aur jab aap ke paas wufad aaein to usey pehna karein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey to wahi pahan sakta hai jiska (aakhirat mein) koi hissey na ho. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas usi qism ke kai hulley aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usmein se aik hulla umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye bhejaa. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke main usey kaisey pahan sakta hun jabke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske mutaalliq pahley manaahii farma chukey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine usey tumhen pahnney ke liye nahi diya balke isliye diya hai ke tum usey bech do ya kisi doosrey ko pehna do chunanche umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo hulla apne aik bhai ko bhej diya jo Makka Mukarrama mein they aur Islam nahi laey they.
5982,"maine Musa-bin-Talha se suna aur unse Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, kaha gaya ke ya Rasulullah ! koi aisa amal bataein jo mujhey jannat mein ley jaey."
5983,"unhon-ne Musa-bin-Talha se suna aur unhon-ne Abu-Ayub Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se ke aik sahib ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! koi aisa amal bataein jo mujhey jannat mein ley jaey. is par logon ne kaha ke usey kya ho gaya hai, usey kya ho gaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kyon ho kya gaya hai? ajii usko zarurat hai bechaara isliye poochhta hai. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke Allah ki ibadat kar aur uske sath kisi aur ko Sharik na kar, Namaz qaaim kar, zakat detey raho aur sila rehmii kartey raho. (bas ye aamaal tujh ko jannat mein ley jaaeinge) chal ab nakel chhod de. rawi ne kaha shayad us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni ontni par Sawar they."
5984,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qata' rehmii karne wala jannat mein nahi jaeyga"
5985,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisey pasand hai ke uski rozii mein faraakhii ho aur uski umr-daraaz ki jaey to wo sila rehmii kya kare."
5986,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo chahta ho ke uske rizq mein faraakhii ho aur uski umr-daraaz ho to wo sila rehmii kya kare.
5987,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ne farmaya Allah Taala ne makhlooq paida ki aur jab us se faraghat hui to raham ne arz kya ke ye us shakhs ki jagah hai jo qata' rehmii se teri panah maangey. Allah Taala ne farmaya ke haan, kya tum is par razi nahi ke main us se jodonga jo tum se apne aapko jodey aur us se tod loonga jo tum se apne aapko tod ley? raham ne kaha kyon nahi, aey rab! Allah Taala ne farmaya ke to ye tujh ko diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad farmaya ke agar tumhara ji chahey to ye aayat padh lo ( فهل عسيتم إن توليتم أن تفسدوا في الأرض وتقطعوا أرحامكم‏ ) yaanii ''kuchh ajeeb nahi ke agar tum ko hukumat mil jaey to tum mulk mein fasaad barpa karo aur rishtey naatey tod daalo.''"
5988,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raham ka talluq Rehman se juda hua hai to jo koi us se apne aapko jodtaa hai Allah paak ne farmaya ke main bhi usko apne se jod leta hun aur jo koi usey todtaa hai main bhi apne aapko us se tod leta hun.
5989,Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raham (rishte-daarii Rehman se mili hui) shaakh hai jo shakhs us se miley mein us se milta hun aur jo us se qata' talluq karey mein us se qata' talluq karta hun.
5990,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke falan ki aulad (yani Abu-Sufiyan bin-Hakam bin Aas ya abu-Lahab ki aulad ( ye Amr bin Abbas ne kaha ke Muhammad-bin-Jafar ki kitab mein us waham par safaid jagah khali thi (yani tahreer na thi) mere azeez nahi hain (go unse nasbi (rishtey ka ( rishta hai) mera wali to Allah hai aur mere azeez to wali hain jo musalmanon mein nek aur parhezgaar hain (go unse nasbi (rishtey ka ( rishta bhi na ho). anbasaa bin abdul-Wahid ne bayaan-bin-bashar se, unhon-ne Qais se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-al-Aas se itna badhaya hai ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya albatta unse mera rishta nataa hai agar wo tar rakhengey to main bhi tar rakhoonga yani wo nataa jodengey to main bhi jodonga."
5991,"Aamash ne ye hadis Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak marfoo nahi bayan ki lekin Hasan aur fitr ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marfooan bayan kya, farmaya ke kisi kaam ka badla dena sila rehmii nahi hai balke sila rehmii karne wala wo hai ke jab uske sath sila rehmii ka mamla na kya ja raha ho tab bhi wo sila rehmii kare."
5992,"ya Rasulullah! aap ka un kaamon ke barey mein kya khayal hai jinhein main ibadat samajh kar zamana jahiliyat mein karta tha maslan sila rehmii, ghulam ki aazaadii, sadqa, kya mujhey un par sawab milega? hakeem (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai tum un tamam aa'maale-khair ke sath Islam laey ho jo pahley kar chukey ho. aur kuchh ne abul-Yamaan se bajaey ( اتحنث ( ke) اتحت ( riwayat kya hai aur Mamar aur Saleh aur ibne- musaafir ne bhi) اتحت ( riwayat kya hai. ibne- Ishaq ne kaha ( اتحنث ( , Mina ( tehet ( se nikla hai iske mana misl aur ibadat karna. Hisham ne bhi apne walid Urwa se un logon ki mutabiat (pairavi) ki hai."
5993,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne walid ke sath hazir hui. mein aik zard qamees pahney huey thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, '' سنہ سنہ '' Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne kaha ke ye habshi zaban mein '' achchha '' ke mana mein hai. Umme- Khalid ne bayan kya ke phir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nabwooat ki mehar se khelney lagi to mere walid ne mujhey daantaa lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey khelney 2 phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum aik zamane tak zinda rahogii Allah Taala tumhari umr khub lambi karey, tumhari zindagi daraaz ho. Abdullah ne bayan kya chunanche unhon-ne bahut hi lambi umr paai aur unki lambi umr ke charchey honey lagey."
5994,"mein ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein maujood tha unse aik shakhs ne (haalate-ehraam mein) machchar ke maarney ke mutaalliq puchha (ke iska kya kaffara hoga) ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne malum farmaya ke tum kahan ke ho? us ne bataya ke Iraq ka, farmaya ke us shakhs ko dekho, (machchar ki jaan leney ke taawaan ka masla poochhta hai) halanke iske mulk walon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nawaasey ko (be-takalluf qatl kar daalaa) maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke ye donon (Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu)) duniya mein mere 2 phool hain."
5995,"mere yahan aik aurat (aur) uske sath 2 bachchiyaan thin, wo maangney aai thi. mere paas se siwa aik khajoor ke usey aur kuchh na mila. maine usey wo khajoor de di aur us ne wo khajoor apni donon ladkiyon ko taqseem kar di. phir uth kar chali gaee iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine aap se iska zikr kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs bhi is tarah ki ladkiyon ki parwarish karega aur unke sath achchha mamla karega to ye uske liye jahannam se parda bin jaaeingii."
5996,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur amaama-binte-abii al-Aas (jo bachchii thiin) wo aap ke shana Mubarak par thin phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi jab aap rukoo kartey to unhein utaar detey aur jab khadey hotey to phir utha letey.
5997,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko bosa diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Aqra-bin-Habis (Raziallahu anhu) baithey huey they. Aqraa (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke mere das ladkey hain aur maine unmein se kisi ko bosa nahi diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki taraf dekha aur farmaya ke jo Allah ki makhlooq par raham nahi karta is par bhi raham nahi kya jata.
5998,"aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha aap log bachchon ko bosa detey hain, ham to unhein bosa nahi detey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar Allah ne tumharey dil se raham nikal diya hai to main kya kar sakta hun."
5999,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh qaidi aaey qaidiyon mein aik aurat thi jiska pistaan doodh se bharaa hua tha aur wo daud rahi thi, itney mein aik bachcha usko qaidiyon mein mila us ne jhat apne pet se laga liya aur usko doodh pilaaney lagi ham se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum khayal kar saktey ho ke ye aurat apne bachchey ko aag mein daal sakti hai. ham ne arz kya ke nahi jab tak usko qudrat hogi ye apne bachchey ko aag mein nahi phenk saktii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke Allah apne bandon par usse bhi zyada raham karne wala hai jitna ye aurat apne bachcha par meharban ho sakti hai."
6000,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ne rehmat ke so hissey banaey aur apne paas unmein se ninyaanwe hissey rakhey sirf aik hissey zameen par utara aur usi ki wjah se tum dekhtey ho ke makhlooq aik doosrey par raham karti hai, yahan tak ke ghodii bhi apne bachche ko apne sum nahi lagney deti balke sumon ko utha leti hai ke kahin us se iske bachcha ko takleef na pahunchey ."
6001,"maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! kon sa gunah sabse bada hai. farmaya ye ke tum Allah Taala ka kisi ko Sharik banao halanke usi ne tumhen paida kya hai. unhon-ne kaha phir, iske baad farmaya ye ke tum apne ladkey ko us khof se qatl karo ke agar zinda raha to tumhari rozii mein Sharik hoga. unhon-ne kaha iske ba'd, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye ke tum apne padosi ki biwi se zina karo. chunanche Allah Taala ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad ki taaiid mein ye aayat والذين لا يدعون مع الله إلها آخر, nazil ki ke ''aur wo log jo Allah ke siwa kisi doosrey maabood ko nahi pukaartey aur na wo nahaq kisi ko qatl kartey hain aur na wo zina kartey hain.''"
6002,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik bachcha (Abdullaah-bin-Zubair) ko apni god mein bithlaayaa aur khajoor chabaa kar iske munh mein di, usne aap par peshab kar diya aap ne pani mangwa kar is par baha diya."
6003,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey apni aik raan par bithatey they aur Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko dusri raan par bithlaatey they. phir donon ko milaate aur farmaatey, aey Allaah! in donon par raham karke main bhi un par raham karta hun aur Ali-bin-Abdullaah madeenii ne bayan kya ke ham se Yahya ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Sulaiman Taimi ne bayan kya, unse abu-Usman nehdi ne usi hadis ko bayan kya. Sulaiman Taimi ne kaha jab abu tameema ne ye hadis mujh se bayan ki abu-Usman nehdi se to mere dil mein shak paida hua. maine abu-Usman se bahut si hadison suni hain par ye hadis kyon nahi suni phir maine apni hadison ki kitab dekhi to usmein ye hadis abu-Usman nehdi se likhi hui thi."
6004,mujhey kisi aurat par itna rashk nahi aata tha jitna Khadija (Raziallahu anha) par aata tha halanke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mujh se shadi se teen saal pahley wafat pa chuki thin. (rashk ki wjah ye thi) ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko main kasarat se unka zikr kartey suntii thi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unke rab ne hukm diya tha ke Khadija ko jannat mein aik khauldaar motiyon ke ghar ki khushkhabri suna dein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kabhi bakri zabah kartey phir usmein se Khadija (Raziallahu anha) ki saheliyon ko hissey bhejtey they.
6005,main aur yateem ki parwarish karne wala jannat mein is tarah hongey aur aap ne shahadat aur darmyani ungliyon ke ishara se ( qurb ko) bataya .
6006,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bewaon aur miskinon ke liye koshish karne wala Allah ke raaste mein jihad karne waley ki tarah hai ya us shakhs ki tarah hai jo din mein rozey rakhta hai aur raat ko ibadat karta hai.
6007,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bewaon aur miskinon ke liye koshish karne wala Allah ke rastey mein jihad karne waley ki tarah hai. Abdullah Qanabi ko usmein shak hai. Imam Malik ne us hadis mein ye bhi kaha tha us shakhs ke barabar sawab milta hai jo Namaz mein khada rehta hai thaktaa hi nahi aur us shakhs ke barabar jo rozey barabar rakhey chala jata hai iftaar hi nahi karta hai.
6008,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Madina hazir huey aur ham sab naujawaan aur ham-Umr they. ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bees dinon tak rahe. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khayal hua ke hamein apne ghar ke log yad aa rahe hongey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se unke mutaalliq puchha jinhein ham apne gharon par chhod kar aaey they. ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Sara haal suna diya. aap badey hi narm khoo aur badey raham karne waley they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apne gharon ko wapas jao aur apne mulk walon ko Deen sikhaao aur bataao aur tum is tarah Namaz padho jis tarah tum ne mujhey Namaz padhtey dekha hai aur jab Namaz ka waqt aa jaey to tum mein se aik shakhs tumharey liye azan de phir jo tum mein bada ho wo imamat karaaey.
6009,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs raaste mein chal raha tha ke usey shiddat ki piyaas lagi usey aik kunwaan mila aur usne usmein utar kar pani piyaa. jab bahar nikla to wahan aik kutta dekha jo haanp raha tha aur piyaas ki wjah se tarii ko chaat raha tha. us shakhs ne kaha ke ye kutta bhi itna hi zyada piyaasaa malum ho raha hai jitna mein tha. chunanche wo phir kuwein mein utra aur apne jootey mein pani bharaa aur munh se pakad kar uper laya aur kuttey ko pani pilaya . Allah Taala ne iske us amal ko pasand farmaya aur uski maghfirat kar di. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! kya hamein janwaron ke sath neki karne mein bhi sawab milta hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen har taaza kalejey waley par neki karne mein sawab milta hai.
6010,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik Namaz ke liye khadey huey aur ham bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khadey huey. Namaz padhtey hi aik dehati ne kaha : aey Allaah! mujh par raham kar aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par aur hamarey sath kisi aur par raham na kar. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne salam phera to dehati se farmaya ke tum ne aik wasee cheez ko tang kar diya aap ki murad Allah ki rehmat se thi.
6011,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mominon ko aapas mein aik doosrey ke sath rehmat w mohabbat ka mamla karne aur aik doosrey ke sath lutf w narm khooi mein aik jism jaisa paogey ke jab iska koi tukda bhi takleef mein hota hai, to Sara jism takleef mein hota hai aisa ke neend ud jati hai aur jism bukhar mein mubtala ho jata hai.''"
6012,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar koi musalman kisi darakht ka paudaa lagata hai aur us darakht se koi insan ya janwar khata hai to lagaaney waley ke liye wo sadqa hota hai.''
6013,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo raham nahi karta is par raham nahi kya jata. ''
6014,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Jibraaiil (Alaihissalam) mujhey padosi ke barey mein baar-baar is tarah wasiiyat kartey rahe ke mujhey khayal guzra ke shayad padosi ko wiraasat mein Sharik na kar dein.''
6015,nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Jibraaiil (Alaihissalam) mujhey padosi ke barey mein baar-baar is tarah wasiiyat kartey rahe ke mujhey khayal guzra ke shayad padosi ko wiraasat mein Sharik na kar dein.''
6016,"aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan kya ''Allah ki qism ! wo eman wala nahi. Allah ki qism ! wo eman wala nahi. Allah ki qism ! wo eman wala nahi. arz kya gaya kon : ya rasoolullaah? farmaya wo jiske shar se iska padosi mehfooz na ho. is hadis ko Shababaa aur Asad bin-Musa ne bhi riwayat kya hai aur Humaid bin Aswad aur Usman bin umr aur Abu-Bakar bin Ayash aur Shuaib bin Ishaq ne us hadis ko ibne-abi-Ze-ib se yun riwayat kya hai, unhon-ne Maqbari se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se."
6017,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ''aey musalman aurton ! tum mein se koi aurat apni kisi padausan ke liye kisi bhi cheez ko (hadiya mein) dene ke liye haqeer na samjhey chahe bakri ka paaya (پایہ) hi kyon na ho.''
6018,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo apne padosi ko takleef na pahunchaaey aur jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo apne mehman ki izzat karey aur jo koi Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo achi baat zaban se nikaley warna khamosh rahe.''
6019,mere kanon ne suna aur meri aankhon ne dekha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) guftgu farma rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo apne padosi ka ikraam karey aur jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo apne mehman ki dastoor ke muwafiq har tarah se izzat kare. puchha : ya Rasulullah ! dastoor ke muwafiq Kab tak hai. farmaya aik din aur aik raat aur mezbaanii teen din ki hai aur jo iske baad ho wo uske liye sadqa hai aur jo Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo behtar baat kahey ya khamosh rahe.
6020,maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri padausanein hain (agar hadiya aik ho to) mein unmein se kis ke paas hadiya bhejoon ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jiska darwaza tum se ( tumharey darwazey se) zyada qareeb ho.''
6021,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har nek kaam sadqa hai.''
6022,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''har musalman par sadqa karna zaroori hai.'' sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya agar koi cheez kisi ko (sadqe ke liye) jo muyassar na ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir apne hath se kaam karey aur us se khud ko bhi fayda pahunchaaey aur sadqa bhi kare. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha agar usmein uski taqat na ho ya kaha ke na kar sakey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir kisi haajat mand pareshan haal ki madad kare. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya agar wo ye bhi na kar sakey. farmaya ke phir bhalai ki taraf logon ko dilchasbi  dilaaey ya Amr bil-ma'aroof ka karna arz kya (bhalaaii ka hukm de) aur agar ye bhi na kar sakey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir burai se ruka rahe ke ye bhi uske liye sadqa hai.
6023,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jahannam ka zikr kya aur us se panah mangi aur chehrey se bachney w na-gawari ka izhar kya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jahannam ka zikr kya aur us se panah mangi aur chehrey se bachney w na-gawari ka izhar kya, Shoba ne bayan kya ke do martaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke jahannam se panah maangney ke silsiley mein mujhey koi shak nahi hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jahannam se bacho . chahe aadhi khajoor hi (kisi ko) sadqa karke ho sakey aur agar kisi ko ye bhi muyassar na ho to achi baat karke hii."
6024,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke kuchh Yahudi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur kaha (السام عليكم‏) (tumhein maut aaey) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke main iska mafhoom samajh gaee aur maine unka jawab diya ke (وعليكم السام واللعنة‏) (yani tumhen maut aaey aur laanat ho) bayan kya ke is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, thehro , aey Aaisha ! Allah Taala tamam maamlaat mein narmii aur mulaaimiyat ko pasand karta hai. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap ne suna nahi unhon-ne kya kaha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine iska jawab de diya tha ke (وعليكم) (aur tumhen bhi)."
6025,aik dehati ne masjid mein peshab kar diya tha. sahaba kiram uski taraf daudey lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iske peshab ko mat roko . phir aap ne pani ka dol mangwaya aur wo peshab ki jagah par baha diya gaya.
6026,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik momin doosrey momin ke liye is tarah hai jaisey Imaarat, ke iska aik hissey doosrey hissey ko thaamey rehta hai) girney nahi deta ( phir aap ne apni ungliyon ko qainchi ki tarah kar liya."
6027,aur aisa hua ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt baithey huey they ke aik sahib ne aa kar sawal kya ya koi zarurat poori karaanii chaahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamari taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya ke tum khamosh kyon baithey rahtey ho balke uski sifarish karo taake tumhen bhi ajr miley aur Allah jo chaahega apne Nabi ki zaban par jari karega (tum apna sawab kyon kho'o).
6028,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jab koi maangney wala ya zarurat mand aata to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke logo! tum sifarish karo taake tumhen bhi sawab miley aur Allah apne Nabi ki zaban par jo chaahega faisla karaaeyga.
6029,"jab Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas Kufa tashrif laey to ham unki khidmat mein hazir huey. unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kya aur batlaya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badgo nahiin they aur na aap bad-zabaan they aur unhon-ne ye bhi bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein sabse behtar wo aadmi hai, jiske akhlaq sabse achchhey hon."
6030,"kuchh Yahudi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan aaey aur kaha ( Assamualaikum . Mina ( (tum par maut aaey ( is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ( عليكم , Mina ولعنكم الله , Mina وغضب الله عليكم‏ . Mina (ke tum par bhi maut aaey aur Allah ki tum par laanat ho aur iska ghazab tum par nazil ho. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ( thehro ( Aaisha ! tumhen narm khooi ikhtiyar karne chahiye sakhti aur bad zabani se bachna chahiye . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne unki baat nahi suni , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne unhein mera jawab nahi suna, maine unki baat unhiin par lota di aur unke haq mein meri baddua qabool ho jaeygi. lekin mere haq mein unki baddua qabool hi na hogi."
6031,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) na gali detey they na buri baat kahnewaaley they na bad-khoo (kisi ka bura chaahney waaley) they aur na laanat malaamat kartey they. agar ham mein se kisi par naraz hotey itna farmatey usey kya ho gaya hai, uski peshani mein khaak lagey."
6032,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik shakhs ne andar aaney ki ijazat chahi . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey dekh kar farmaya ke bura hai falan qabeele ka bhaaii. ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (ke bura hai falan qabeele ka betaa. phir jab wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa betha to aap iske sath bahut achchey akhlaq ke sath pesh aaey. wo shakhs jab chala gaya to Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne aap se arz kya : ya Rasulullah! jab aap ne usey dekha tha to iske mutaalliq ye kalimaat farmaai they, jab aap us se miley to bahut hi khanda peshani se miley. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Aaisha ! tum ne mujhey bad-go Kab paya. Allah ke yahan qiyamat ke din wo log badtareen hongey jinke shar ke dar se log us se milnaa chhod dein."
6033,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sabse zyada khoobsoorat, sabse zyada data aur sabse zyada bahaadur they. aik raat Madina waley (shahar ke bahar shor sun kar) ghabraa gaey. (ke shayad dushman ne hamla kya hai) sab log us shor ki taraf badhey. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) awaz ki taraf badhney walon mein sabse aagey they aur farmatey jatey they ke koi dar ki baat nahi, koi dar ki baat nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt abu-Talha ke) mandoob naamii) ghodey ki nangii peeth par Sawar they, is par koi zeen nahi thi aur galey mein talwaar latak rahi thi. aap ne farmaya ke maine us ghodey ko samandar paya ya farmaya ke ye tez daudney mein samandar ki tarah tha."
6034,kabhi aisa nahi hua ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kisi ne koi cheez mangi ho aur aap ne iske deney se inkar kya ho.
6035,"ham Abdullah-bin-Amr ke paas baithey huey they, wo ham se baatein kar rahe they usi doran unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) na bad-go they na bad zabani kartey they (ke munh se gaaliyaan nikaalein) balke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ke tum mein sabse zyada behtar wo hai jiske akhlaq sabse achchhey hon."
6036,"aik khatun Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein ''burda'' lekar aaein phir Sehal ne maujood logon se kaha tumhen malum hai, ke burda kya cheez hai? logon ne kaha ke burda shamla ko kehtey hain. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke haan, lungii jis mein haashiya bana hua hota hai to us khatun ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! main ye lungii aap ke pahnney ke liye laai hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo lungii unse qabool kar li. us waqt aapko uski zarurat bhi thi phir aap ne pahan liya. sahaba mein se aik sahabi Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke badan par wo lungii dekhii to arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye badi umda lungii hai, aap mujhey usko inayat farma dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ley lo, jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se uth kar tashrif le gaey to andar ja kar wo lungii badal kar teh karke Abdur-Rehman ko bhej di to logon ne un sahib ko malaamat se kaha ke tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se lungii maang kar achchha nahi kya, tum ne dekh liya tha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey is tarah qabool kya tha maano aapko uski zarurat thi. iske bawajud tum ne lungii nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maangii, halanke tumhen malum hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jab bhi koi cheez mangi jati hai to aap inkar nahi kartey. us sahabi ne arz kya ke main to sirf uski barkat ka ummeedwaar hun ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey pahan chukey they meri gharaz ye thi ke main us lungii mein kafan diya jaaunga."
6037,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' zamana jaldi jaldii guzrega aur Deen ka ilm duniya mein kam ho jaeyga aur dilon mein kanjoosii samaa jaeygi aur ladai badh jaaeygii.'' sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ( هرج ( kya hota hai? farmaya qatl khoon-rezii .
6038,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki das saal tak khidmat ki lekin aap ne kabhi mujhey uff tak nahi kaha aur na kabhi ye kaha ke falan kaam kyon kya aur falan kaam kyon nahi kya.
6039,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ghar mein kya kartey they? farmaya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ghar ke kaam kaaj kartey aur jab Namaz ka waqt ho jata to Namaz ke liye masjid tashrif ley jatey they.
6040,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jab Allah kisi bande se mohabbat karta hai to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ko awaz deta hai ke Allah falan bandey se mohabbat karta hai tum bhi us se mohabbat karo. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) bhi us se mohabbat karne lagtey hain, phir wo tamam aasman walon mein awaz detey hain ke Allah falan bandey se mohabbat karta hai. tum bhi us se mohabbat karo. phir tamam aasman waley us se mohabbat karne lagtey hain. iske baad wo zameen mein bhi (Allah ke bandon ka ( maqbool aur mahboob bin jata hai."
6041,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shakhs eman ki halaawat ( mithas (us waqt tak nahi pa sakta jab tak wo kisi shakhs se mohabbat karey to sirf Allah ke liye karey aur usko aag mein daala jana achchha lagey lekin eman ke baad kufr mein jana usey pasand na ho, aur jab tak Allah aur uske rasool se usey unke siwa dusri tamam chizon ke muqaabley mein zyada mohabbat na ho."
6042,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi ki reeh khaarij honey par hansney se mana farmaya aur aap ne ye bhi farmaya ke tum mein se kis tarah aik shakhs apni biwi ko zor se maarta hai jaisey oont , halanke uski poori ummeed hai ke Sham mein usey wo galey lagaaeyga aur sory, Wuhaib aur abu-Muawia ne Hisham se bayan kya ke) janwar ki tarah) ke bajaey lafz ghulam ki tarah ka istemal kya."
6043,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (hijjatul-wadaa (ke mauqe par Mina mein farmaya tum jantey ho ye kon sa din hai? sahaba boley Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai. farmaya ye hurmat wala din hai) phir farmaya ( tum jantey ho ye kon sa Shahar hai? sahaba boley Allah aur us rasool ko zyada ilm hai, farmaya ye hurmat wala Shahar hai. ( phir farmaya ( tum jantey ho ye kon sa mahina hai? sahaba boley Allah aur uske rasool ko zyada ilm hai, farmaya yahi hurmat wala mahina hai. phir farmaya bila shubah Allah ne tum par tumhara (eik doosrey ka ( khoon, maal aur izzat isi tarah haram kya hai jaisey is din ko us ne tumharey us maheene mein aur tumharey is Shahar mein hurmat wala banaya hai."
6044,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''muslmaan ko gali dena gunah hai aur usko qatl karna kufr hai.'' ghandar ne Shoba se riwayat karne mein Sulaiman ki mutabiat (pairavi) ki hai.
6045,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar koi shakhs kisi shakhs ko kaafir ya fasiq kahey aur wo dar-haqiqat kaafir ya fasiq na ho to khud kehney wala fasiq aur kaafir ho jaeyga"
6046,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fahash bhale hi nahi they, na aap laanat malaamat karne waley they aur na gali detey they, aapko bahut ghussa aata to sirf itna keh detey, usey kya ho gaya hai, uski peshani pe khaak lagey."
6047,"Sabit bin Suhak (Raziallahu anhu) Ashaabe-shajar (baite-rizwan karne waalon) mein se they, unhon-ne unse bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo Islam ke siwa kisi aur mazhab par qism khaaey (ke agar maine falan kaam kya to main nasrani hun, Yahudi hun) to wo aisa ho jaeyga jaisey ke usne kaha aur kisi insan par un chizon ki nazar sahi nahi hoti jo iske ikhtiyar mein na hon aur jisne duniya mein kisi cheez se khudkushii kar li usey usi cheez se aakhirat mein azab hoga aur jisne kisi musalman par laanat bheji to ye iske khoon karne ke barabar hai aur jo shakhs kisi musalman ko kaafir kahey to wo aisa hai jaisey uska khoon kya."
6048,"maine Sulaiman bin-Surad se suna wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi hain, unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney 2 aadmiyon ne aapas mein gali galoch ki aik sahib ko ghussa aa gaya aur bahut zyada aaya, unka chehra phool gaya aur rang badal diya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt farmaya ke mujhey aik kalima malum hai ke agar (ghussa karne wala shakhs) usey keh ley to uska ghussa door ho jaeyga chunanche aik sahib ne ja kar ghussa hone-waale ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka irshad sunaya aur kaha shaitan se Allah ki panah maang wo kehney laga kya tum mujh ko bimar samajhtey ho ya deewaanaa ? ja apna rasta ley."
6049,"mujh se Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ko lailatul-Qadr ki bashaarat dene ke liye hujrey se bahar tashrif laaey, lekin musalmanon ke 2 aadmi us waqt aapas mein kisi baat par ladney lagey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhen ( lailatul-Qadr ke mutaalliq ( bataaney ke liye nikla tha lekin falan-falan aapas mein ladney lagey aur) mere ilm se) wo utha li gaee. mumkin hai ke yahi tumharey liye achchha ho. ab tum usey 29 Ramazan aur 27 Ramazan aur 25 Ramazan ki raaton mein talash karo."
6050,"maine Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke jism par aik chadar dekhi aur unke ghulam ke jism par bhi aik waisii hi chadar thi, maine arz kya : agar apne ghulam ki chadar ley lein aur usey bhi pahan lein to aik rang ka joda ho jaey ghulam ko doosra kapda de dein. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke mujh main aur aik sahib ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu)) mein takraar ho gaee thi to unki maan ajamii thin, maine is barey mein unko ta'na de diya unhon-ne ja kar ye baat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se keh di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya kya tum ne us se jhagdaa kya hai? maine arz kya ji haan. malum kya tum ne usey uski maa ki wjah se ta'na diya hai? maine arz kya ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey andar abhi jahiliyat ki bo baqi hai. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! is budhapey mein bhi? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, yad rakho ye ( ghulam bhi) tumharey bhai hain, Allah Taala ne unhein tumhari ma-tehti mein diya hai, to Allah Taala jiski ma-tehti mein bhi iske bhai ko rakhey usey chahiye ke jo wo khaaey usey bhi khilaey aur jo wo pahney usey bhi pehnaey aur usey aisa kaam karne ke liye na kahey, jo uske bas mein na ho agar usey koi aisa kaam karne ke liye kehna hi padey to us kaam mein uski madad kare."
6051,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Zohar ki Namaz 2 rakaat padhai aur salam pher diya iske baad aap masjid ke aagey ke hisse yani daalaan mein aik lakdi par sahara lekar khadey ho gaey aur is par apna hath rakha , haaziriin mein Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they magar aap ke dabdabey ki wjah se kuchh bol na sakey aur jald baaz log masjid se bahar nikal gaey aapas mein sahaba ne kaha ke shayad Namaz mein rakaat kam ho gain hain isi liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz char ke bajaey sirf 2 hi rakaat padhaaein hain. haaziriin mein aik sahabi they jinhein aap zul-yadain ( lambey hathon wala ( keh kar mukhaatab farmaya kartey they, unhon-ne arz kya : aey Allah ke Nabi ! Namaz ki rakaat kam ho gain hain ya aap bhool gaey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke na main bhula hun aur na Namaz ki rakaat kam huin hain. sahaba ne arz kya : nahi ya Rasulullah! aap bhool gaey hain, chunanche aap ne yad karke farmaya ke zul-yadain ne sahi kaha hai. phir aap khadey huey aur 2 rakaat aur padhaaein phir salam phera aur takbeer keh kar sajda (sajda sahw) mein gaey, Namaz ke sajde ki tarah balke us se bhi zyada lamba sajda kya phir sar uthaya aur takbeer keh kar phir sajde mein gaey pahley sajde ki tarah ya us se bhi lambaa, phir sar uthaya aur takbeer kahi."
6052,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) 2 qabron ke paas se guzrey aur farmaya ke un donon mardon ko azab ho raha hai aur ye kisi badey gunah ki wjah se azab mein giraftaar nahi hain balke ye (eik qabr ka murda) apne peshab ki chheenton se nahi bachta tha (ya peshab kartey waqt parda nahi karta tha) aur ye (doosri qabr wala murda) chughal khor tha, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik harii shaakh mangaaii aur usey 2 tukdon mein tod kar donon qabron par gaad diya iske baad farmaya ke jab tak ye shakhein sookh na jayen us waqt tak shayad un donon ka azab halka rahe."
6053,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qabeela Ansar mein sabse behtar gharaana banu-Najjaar ka gharaana hai.''
6054,"aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se andar aaney ki ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ijazat de do, falan qabila ka ye bura aadmi hai jab wo shakhs andar aaya to aap ne iske sath badi narmii se guftgu ki. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aapko iske mutaalliq jo kuchh kehna tha wo irshad farmaya aur phir iske sath narm guftgu ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Aaisha ! wo badtareen aadmi hai jisey uski bad-kalaamii ke dar se log (usey) chhod dein."
6055,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina Munawra ke kisi baagh se tashrif laey to aap ne 2 ( murda ( insanon ki awaz suni jinhein unki qabron mein azab diya ja raha tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein azab ho raha hai aur kisi badey gunah ki wjah se unhein azab nahi ho raha hai. unmein se aik shakhs peshab ki chheenton se nahi bachta tha aur doosra chughal khor tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ki aik harii shaakh mangwai aur usey 2 hisson mein todaa aur aik tukda aik ki qabr par aur doosra doosrey ki qabr par gaad diya. phir farmaya shayad ke unke azab mein us waqt tak ke liye kami kar di jaey, jab tak ye sookh na jaaein."
6056,"ham Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas maujood they, unse kaha gaya ke aik shakhs aisa hai jo yahan ki baatein Usman se ja lagata hai. is par Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne batlaya ke jannat mein chughal khor nahi jaeyga"
6057,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs ( roze ki haalat mein) jhoot baat karna aur faraib karna aur jahaalat ki baton ko na chhodey to Allah ko iski koi zarurat nahi ke wo apna khana peenaa chhodey . Ahmed bin Yunus ne kaha ye hadis maine suni to thi magar main iski sanad bhool gaya tha jo mujh ko aik shakhs ( ibne-abi-Ze-ib ( ne batla di.
6058,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum qiyamat ke din Allah ke yahan us shakhs ko sabse badtar paogey jo kuchh logon ke samney aik rukh se aata hai aur dusron ke samney doosrey rukh se jata hai.
6059,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh maal taqseem kya to Ansar mein se aik shakhs ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us taqseem se Allah ki raza maqsud na thi. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho kar us shakhs ki ye baat aapko sunai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Musa (Alaihissalam) par raham karey, unhein is se bhi zyada eiizaa di gaee, lekin unhon-ne sabr kya."
6060,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne suna ke aik shakhs doosrey shakhs ki tareef kar raha hai aur tareef mein bahut mubaalghe se kaam ley raha tha (yaani bahut badha-chadhaakar tareef kar raha tha) to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ne usey halaak kar diya ya (ye farmaya ke) tum ne us shakhs ki kamar ko tod diya.
6061,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein aik shakhs ka zikr aaya to aik doosrey shakhs ne unki bahut zyada tareef ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke afsos tum ne apne sathi ki gardan tod di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye jumla kai baar farmaya, agar tumharey liye kisi ki tareef karni zaroori ho to ye kehna chahiye ke main iske mutaalliq aisa khayal karta hun, baqi ilm Allah ko hai wo aisa hai. agar usko ye malum ho ke wo aisa hi hai aur yun na kahey ke wo Allah ke nazdeek achchha hi hai. aur Wuhaib ne isi sanad ke sath Khalid se yun riwayat ki arey teri kharabi tu ney uski gardan kaat dali yani lafz ( ويحك (ke bajaey lafz ( ويلك ( bayan kya."
6062,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko izaar latkaaney ke barey mein jo kuchh farmana tha jab aap ne farmaya to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! mera tahmad aik taraf se latakney lagta hai, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum un takabbur karne walon mein se nahi ho."
6063,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) itney itney dinon tak is haal mein rahe ke aapko khayal hota tha ke jaisey aap apni biwi ke paas ja rahe hain halanke aisa nahi tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se aik din farmaya, Aaisha! maine Allah Taala se aik maamle mein sawal kya tha aur us ne wo baat mujhey batla di, 2 Farishtey mere paas aaey, aik mere paon ke paas baith gaya aur doosra sar ke paas baith gaya. us ne us se kaha ke jo mere sar ke paas tha un sahib (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ka kya haal hai? doosrey ne jawab diya ke un par jaadoo kar diya gaya hai. poochha, kis ne un par jaadoo kya hai? jawab diya ke Labid bin A'sam ne. poochha, kis cheez mein kya hai. jawab diya ke nar khajoor ke khosha ke ghilaaf mein, iske andar kanghi hai aur kataan ke taar hain. aur ye doran ke kuwein mein aik chattaan ke nichey daba diya hai. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif le gaey aur farmaya ke yahi wo kunwaan hai jo mujhey khuwab mein dikhlaaya gaya tha. iske baagh ke darakhton ke pattey saanpon ke phan jaisey daraawney malum hotey hain aur uska pani mahndii ke nichodey huey pani ki tarah surkh tha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se wo jaadoo nikala gaya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! phir kyon nahi, unki murad ye thi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqia ko shohrat kyon na di. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey Allah ne shifa de di hai aur main un logon mein khah-m-khah burai ke phailaaney ko pasand nahi karta. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Labid bin A'sam yahood ke haleef bani zuraiq se talluq rakhta tha."
6064,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' bad-gumaanii se bachtey raho kyonke bad-gumaanii ki baatein aksar jhooti hoti hain, logon ke uyoob talash karne ke peechhey na pado, aapas mein hasad na karo, kisi ki peeth peechhey burai na karo, bughz na rakho, balke sab Allah ke bandey aapas mein bhai bhai bin kar raho.''"
6065,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' aapas mein bughz na rakho, hasad na karo, peeth peechhey kisi ki burai na karo, balke Allah ke bandey aapas mein bhai bhai bin kar raho aur kisi musalman ke liye jaaiz nahi ke aik bhai kisi bhai se teen din se zyada salam kalam chhod kar rahe.''"
6066,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''bad-gumaanii se bachtey raho, bad-gumaanii aksar tahqeeq ke baad jhooti baat Sabit hoti hai aur kisi ke uyoob dhoondney ke peechhey na pado , kisi ka aib khah-m-khah mat tatolo aur kisi ke bhaaw par bhaaw na badhaao aur hasad na karo, bughz na rakho, kisi ki peeth peechhey burai na karo balke sab Allah ke bandey aapas mein bhai bhai bin kar raho.''"
6067,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main guman karta hun ke falan aur falan hamarey Deen ki koi baat nahi jantey hain.'' Lais-bin-Sad ne bayan kya ke ye donon aadmi munafiq they.
6068,aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey aur farmaya Aaisha mein guman karta hun ke falan-falan log ham jis Deen par hain usko nahi pehchantey .
6069,"maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri tamam ummat ko maaf kya jaeyga siwa gunahon ko khullam-khullaa karne walon ke aur gunahon ko khullam-khullaa karne mein ye bhi shamil hai ke aik shakhs raat ko koi (gunaah ka ( kaam karey aur iske bawajud ke Allah ne uske gunah ko chipa diya hai magar subah honey par wo kehney lagey ke aey fulaan! maine kal raat falan-falan bura kaam kya tha. raat guzar gaee thi aur uske rab ne uska gunah chhipaaey rakhaa, lekin jab subah hui to wo khud Allah ke pardey ko kholney laga."
6070,"aik shakhs ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaanaa-phoosii ke barey mein kya suna hai? (yani sargoshi ke barey mein) unhon-ne kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they (qiyamat ke din tum muslmaanon) mein se aik shakhs (jo gunahgaar hoga) apne parwardigar se nazdeek ho jaeyga parwardigar apna bazu is par rakh dega aur farmaeyga tu ney (fulaan din duniya mein) ye-ye burey kaam kiye they, wo arz karega. beshak (parwardigaar mujh se khataein hui hain par to ghafoor-raheem hai) gharaz ( sarey gunahon ka (us se (pahley) iqrar kara lega phir farmaeyga dekh maine duniya mein terey gunah chhipaaey rakhey to aaj main un gunahon ko bakhsh deta hun."
6071,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen jannat walon ki khabar na dun. har kamzor w tawaazeh karne wala agar wo (Allah ka naam lekar) qism kha ley to Allah uski qism poori kar de. kya main tumhen dozakh walon ki khabar na dun har tund khoo, akad kar chalney wala aur mutakabbir."
6072,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke akhlaq faazila ka ye haal tha ke aik londi Madina ki laundiyon mein se aap ka hath pakad leti aur apne kisi bhi kaam ke liye jahan chahti aapko ley jati thi.
6073,"wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke maadrii bhatijey they, unhon-ne kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne koi cheez bheji ya khairat ki to Abdullah-bin-Zubair jo unke bhaanjey they kehney lagey ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko aisey muaamlon se baaz rehna chahiye nahi to Allah ki qism main unke liye hijr ka hukm jari kar doonga . Ummul-Momenin ne kaha kya usne ye alfaz kahey hain? logon ne bataya ke ji haan. farmaya phir main Allah se nazar karti hun ke ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se ab kabhi nahi boloongii. iske baad jab unke qata' ta'lluqii par arsa guzar gaya. to Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye unse sifarish ki gaee (ke unhein maaf farma dein ( Ummul-Momenin ne kaha hargiz nahi, Allah ki qasam! uske barey mein koi sifarish nahi maanoongii aur apni nazar nahi todoongii. jab ye qatae talluq Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye bahut takleef deh ho gaee to unhon-ne Miswar-bin-Makhrama aur Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Aswad bin abd Yaghoos (Raziallahu anhu) se is silsiley mein baat ki wo donon bani zohra se talluq rakhtey they. unhon-ne unse kaha ke main tumhen Allah ka waasta deta hun kisi tarah tum log mujhey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre mein dakhil kara 2 kyonke unke liye ye jaaiz nahi ke mere sath sila rehmii ko todney ki qism khaaein chunanche Miswar aur Abdur-Rehman donon apni chaadaron mein liptey huey Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko usmein sath lekar aaey aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se andar aaney ki ijazat chahi aur kaha Assalaamu alaikum warahmatullahi wabarkaatuh , kya ham andar aa saktey hain? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha aa jao . unhon-ne arz kya ham sab ? kaha haan , sab aa jao . Ummul-Momenin ko iska ilm nahi tha ke Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unke sath hain. jab ye andar gaey to Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) parda hata kar andar chaley gaey aur Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) se lipat kar Allah ka waasta dene lagey aur roney lagey (ke maaf kar dein, ye Ummul-Momenin ke bhaanjey they) Miswar aur Abdur-Rehman bhi Ummul-Momenin ko Allah ka waasta dene lagey ke Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se bolein aur unhein maaf kar dein un hazraat ne ye bhi arz kya ke jaisa ke tum ko malum hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne talluq todney se mana kya hai ke kisi musalman ke liye jaaiz nahi ke kisi apne bhai se teen din se zyada wali hadis yad dilaane lagey aur ye ke usmein nuqsan hai to Ummul-Momenin bhi unhein yad dilaane lagiin aur roney lagiin aur farmaney lagiin ke maine to qism kha li hai? aur qism ka mamla sakht hai lekin ye buzurg log barabar koshish kartey rahe, yahan tak ke Ummul-Momenin ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se baat kar li aur apni qism ( todney ( ki wjah se chalis (40) ghulam aazad kiye. iske baad jab bhi aap ye qism yad kartin to roney lagtiin aur aap ka dupatta aansuon se tar ho jata."
6074,"wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke maadrii bhatijey they, unhon-ne kaha ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne koi cheez bheji ya khairat ki to Abdullah-bin-Zubair jo unke bhaanjey they kehney lagey ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko aisey muaamlon se baaz rehna chahiye nahi to Allah ki qism main unke liye hijr ka hukm jari kar doonga . Ummul-Momenin ne kaha kya usne ye alfaz kahey hain? logon ne bataya ke ji haan. farmaya phir main Allah se nazar karti hun ke ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se ab kabhi nahi boloongii. iske baad jab unke qata' ta'lluqii par arsa guzar gaya. to Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye unse sifarish ki gaee (ke unhein maaf farma dein ( Ummul-Momenin ne kaha hargiz nahi, Allah ki qasam! uske barey mein koi sifarish nahi maanoongii aur apni nazar nahi todoongii. jab ye qatae talluq Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye bahut takleef deh ho gaee to unhon-ne Miswar-bin-Makhrama aur Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Aswad bin abd Yaghoos (Raziallahu anhu) se is silsiley mein baat ki wo donon bani zohra se talluq rakhtey they. unhon-ne unse kaha ke main tumhen Allah ka waasta deta hun kisi tarah tum log mujhey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre mein dakhil kara 2 kyonke unke liye ye jaaiz nahi ke mere sath sila rehmii ko todney ki qism khaaein chunanche Miswar aur Abdur-Rehman donon apni chaadaron mein liptey huey Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko usmein sath lekar aaey aur Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se andar aaney ki ijazat chahi aur kaha Assalaamu alaikum warahmatullahi wabarkaatuh , kya ham andar aa saktey hain? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha aa jao . unhon-ne arz kya ham sab ? kaha haan , sab aa jao . Ummul-Momenin ko iska ilm nahi tha ke Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) bhi unke sath hain. jab ye andar gaey to Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) parda hata kar andar chaley gaey aur Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) se lipat kar Allah ka waasta dene lagey aur roney lagey (ke maaf kar dein, ye Ummul-Momenin ke bhaanjey they) Miswar aur Abdur-Rehman bhi Ummul-Momenin ko Allah ka waasta dene lagey ke Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se bolein aur unhein maaf kar dein un hazraat ne ye bhi arz kya ke jaisa ke tum ko malum hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne talluq todney se mana kya hai ke kisi musalman ke liye jaaiz nahi ke kisi apne bhai se teen din se zyada wali hadis yad dilaane lagey aur ye ke usmein nuqsan hai to Ummul-Momenin bhi unhein yad dilaane lagiin aur roney lagiin aur farmaney lagiin ke maine to qism kha li hai? aur qism ka mamla sakht hai lekin ye buzurg log barabar koshish kartey rahe, yahan tak ke Ummul-Momenin ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se baat kar li aur apni qism ( todney ( ki wjah se chalis (40) ghulam aazad kiye. iske baad jab bhi aap ye qism yad kartin to roney lagtiin aur aap ka dupatta aansuon se tar ho jaataa."
