kar dein, ye Ummul-Momenin ke bhaanjey they) Miswar aur Abdur-Rehman bhi Ummul-Momenin ko Allah ka waasta dene lagey ke Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se bolein aur unhein maaf kar dein un hazraat ne ye bhi arz kya ke jaisa ke tum ko malum hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne talluq todney se mana kya hai ke kisi musalman ke liye jaaiz nahi ke kisi apne bhai se teen din se zyada wali hadis yad dilaane lagey aur ye ke usmein nuqsan hai to Ummul-Momenin bhi unhein yad dilaane lagiin aur roney lagiin aur farmaney lagiin ke maine to qism kha li hai? aur qism ka mamla sakht hai lekin ye buzurg log barabar koshish kartey rahe, yahan tak ke Ummul-Momenin ne Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se baat kar li aur apni qism ( todney ( ki wjah se chalis (40) ghulam aazad kiye. iske baad jab bhi aap ye qism yad kartin to roney lagtiin aur aap ka dupatta aansuon se tar ho jaataa."
6076,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' aapas mein bughz na rakho aur aik doosrey se hasad na karo, peeth peechhey kisi ki burai na karo, balke Allah ke bandey aur aapas mein bhaaii-bhaaii bin kar raho aur kisi musalman ke liye jaaiz nahi ke kisi bhai se teen din se zyada tak baat cheet band kare. ''"
6077,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kisi shakhs ke liye jaaiz nahi ke apne kisi bhai se teen din se zyada ke liye mulaqat chhodey, Is tarah ke jab donon ka saamnaa ho jaey to ye bhi munh pher ley aur wo bhi munh pher ley aur un donon mein behtar wo hai jo salam mein pahal kare.''"
6078,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''main tumhari narazagi aur khushi ko khub pehchanta hun. Ummul-Momenin ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap kis tarah se pehchantey hain? farmaya ke jab tum khush hoti ho kehti ho, haan Muhammad ke rab ki qasam! aur jab naraz hoti ho to kehti ho nahi, Ibrahim ke rab ki qasam! bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ji haan, aap ka farmana bilkul sahi hai main sirf aap ka naam lena chhodtii hun."
6079,"jab maine hosh sanbhaalaa to apne waalidain ko Deen Islam ka pairo paya aur koi din aisa nahi guzarta tha ke jis main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas subah w Sham tashrif na latey hon, aik din Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu)) walid maajid ( ghar mein bhari do-pahar mein baithey huey they ke aik shakhs ne kaha ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif la rahe hain, ye aisa waqt tha ke us waqt hamarey yahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aaney ka mamool (routine) nahi tha, Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke Is waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tashrif lana kisi khas wjah hi se ho sakta hai, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey Makka chhodney ki ijazat mil gaee hai."
6080,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qabila Ansar ke gharaanE mein mulaqat ke liye tashrif le gaey aur unhIin ke yahan khana khaayaa, jab aap wapas tashrif laney lagey to aap ke hukm se aik chatai par pani chhidkaa gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par Namaz padhi aur ghar walon ke liye dua ki."
6081,"mujh se Salim bin-Abdullah ne puchha ke) إستبرق ( kya cheez hai? maine kaha ke deebaa se bana hua mota aur khurdaraa kapdaa, phir unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik shakhs ko istibraq ka joda pahney huey dekha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein usey lekar hazir huey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! usey aap khareed lein aur wafad jab aap se mulaqat ke liye aaein to unki mulaqat ke waqt usey pahan liya karein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke resham to wahi pahan sakta hai jiska (aakhirat mein) koi hissey na ho khair is baat par aik muddat guzar gaee phir aisa hua ke aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud unhein aik joda bheja to wo usey lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya aap ne ye joda mere liye bheja hai, halanke iske barey mein aap us se pahley aisa irshad farma chukey hain? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye maine tumharey paas isliye bheja hai taake tum iske zariey (bech kar) maal hasil karo. chunanche ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) isi hadis ki wjah se kapdey main (resham ke) beil-booton ko bhi makruh jantey they."
6082,jab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf hamarey yahan aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein aur Sad-bin-Rabee mein bhaaii-chaargii karaai to phir (jab Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne nikah kya to) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab walima kar chahe aik bakri ka ho.
6083,"ham se Muhammad-bin Sabaah ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Ismail bin Zakariya ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Aasim bin Sulaiman ahwal ne bayan kya, kaha ke maine Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, kya tum ko ye baat malum hai ke Islaam mein muaahide (half) ki koi asl nahi? Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud quraish aur Ansar ke darmyan mere ghar mein half karaai thii."
6084,"Rifaa Qarzi ne apni biwi ko talaaq de di aur talaaq rajaii nahi di. iske baad unse Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne nikah kar liya, lekin wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main Rifaa (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thi lekin unhon-ne mujhey teen talaaqein de dein. phir mujh se Abdur-Rehman bin Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne nikah kar liya, lekin Allah ki qism unke paas to pallu ki tarah ke siwa aur kuchh nahi. ( murad ye ke wo naa-mard hain) aur unhon-ne apne chadar ka pallu pakad kar bataya ( rawi ne bayan kya ke) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they aur Saeed-bin-al-Aas ke ladkey Khalid hujre ke darwazey par they aur andar dakhil honey ki ijazat ke intezar mein they. Khalid-bin Saeed is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko awaz de kar kehney lagey ke aap us aurat ko daant'tey nahi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney kis tarah ki baat kehti hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tabassum ke siwa aur kuchh nahi farmaya, phir farmaya, ghaaliban tum Rifaa ke paas dobara jana chahti ho lekin ye us waqt tak mumkin nahi hai jab tak tum unka (Abdur-Rehmaan (Raziallahu anhu) ka ( mazaa na chakh lo aur wo tumhara maza na chakh lein."
6085,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honey ki ijazat chahi . us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aap ki kai beeviyan jo Quraish se talluq rakhti thin aap se kharch dene ke liye taqaza kar rahi thin aur unchi awaz mein baatein kar rahi thin. jab umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ijazat chahi to wo jaldi se bhag kar pardey ke peechhey chali gain . phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko ijazat di aur wo dakhil huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt hans rahe they, umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : Allah aapko khush rakhey , ya Rasulullah ! mere maan-baap aap par qurbaan hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un par mujhey hairat hui, jo abhi mere paas taqaza kar rahi thin, jab unhon-ne tumhari awaz suni to fauran bhag kar pardey ke peechhey chali gain . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap iske zyada mustahiq hain ke aap se dara jaey, phir aurton ko mukhaatab karke unhon-ne kaha, apni jaanon ki dushman ! mujh se to tum dartii ho aur Allah ke rasool se nahi darteen . unhon-ne arz kya : aap Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada sakht hain. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan aey ibne-khattaab ! us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, agar shaitan bhi tumhen rastey par aata hua dekhega to tumhara rasta chhod kar doosrey rastey par chala jaeyga"
6086,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Taaif mein they (fatah Makka ke baad) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar Allah ne chaha to ham yahan se kal wapas hongey. aap ke kuchh sahaba ne kaha ke ham us waqt tak nahi jaeinge jab tak usey fateh na kar lein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar yahi baat hai to kal subah ladai karo. bayan kya ke doosrey din subah ko sahaba ne ghamasaan ki ladai ladii aur kasrat se sahaba zakhmi huey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke inshaAllah ham kal wapas hongey. bayan kya ke ab sab log khamosh rahe. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans padey. Humaidii ne bayan kya ke ham se Sufiyan ne poori sanad (khabar) ke lafz ke sath bayan ki.
6087,"aik sahib Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : main to tabah ho gaya apni biwi ke sath Ramazan mein (roze ki haalat mein) ham-bistarii kar li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir aik ghulam aazad kar. unhon-ne arz kya : mere paas koi ghulam nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir do mahiney ke rozey rakh. unhon-ne arz kya : uski mujh mein taqat nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir sath (60) miskinon ko khana khilaa . unhon-ne arz kya ke itna bhi mere paas nahi hai. bayan kya ke phir khajoor ka aik tokraa laya gaya. Ibrahim ne bayan kya ke (arq) aik tarah ka (nau (9) kilogram ka ( aik paimaana tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke poochhney wala kahan hai? lo usey sadqa kar dena. unhon-ne arz kya mujh se, jo zyada mohtaaj ho usey dun? Allah ki qism ! Madina ke donon maidaanon ke darmyan koi gharaana bhi ham se zyada mohtaaj nahi hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans diye aur aap ke samney ke dandaaney Mubarak khul gaey. iske baad farmaya ke achchha phir to tum miyan biwi hi usey kha lo."
6088,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chal raha tha. aap ke jism par aik najraanii chadar thi, jiska haashiya mota tha. itney mein aik dehati Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur us ne aap ki chadar badey zor se khinchi . Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke shaaney ko dekha ke zor se kheenchney ki wjah se, is par nishan pad gaey. phir usne kaha : aey Muhammad ! Allah ka jo maal aap ke paas hai is mein se mujhey diye janey ka hukm farmaiye . us waqt maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mud kar dekha to aap muskuraa diye phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey diye janey ka hukm farmaayaa."
6089,jab se maine Islam qabool kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apne paas aaney se) kabhi nahi rokaa aur jab bhi aap ne mujhey dekha to muskuraaey.
6090,"main ghodey par jam kar nahi baith paata to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath mere seeney par maara aur dua ki (اللهم ثبته واجعله هاديا مهديا ( ''aey Allah ! isey mazbooti farma, isey hidayat karne wala aur khud hidayat paya hua banaa.''"
6091,"Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Allah haq se nahi sharmaataa , kya aurat ko jab ehtilam ho to is par ghusl wajib hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, jab aurat pani dekhey (to is par ghusl wajib hai) is par Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) hanseiin aur arz kya, kya aurat ko bhi ehtilam hota hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir bachchey ki sura maan se kyon miltii hai?"
6092,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is tarah khul kar kabhi hanstey nahi dekha ke aap ke halaq ka kowa nazar aaney lagta ho, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sirf muskuratey they."
6093,"aik sahib Juma ke din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt Madina mein Juma ka khutba de rahe they. unhon-ne arz kya barish ka qahat (sukhaa) pad gaya hai. aap apne rab se barish ki dua keejiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aasman ki taraf dekha kahin hamein badal nazar nahi aa raha tha. phir aap ne barish ki dua ki. itney mein badal utha aur kuchh tukdey kuchh ki taraf badhey aur barish honey lagi yahan tak ke Madina ke naley bahney lagey. agley Juma tak isi tarah barish hoti rahi silsila tut'taa (ٹوٹتا) hi na tha chunanche wahi sahib ya koi doosrey (agley Juma ko) khadey huey, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba de rahe they aur unhon-ne arz kya : ham doob gaey, apne rab se dua karein ke ab barish band kar de. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey Allah ! hamarey charon taraf barish ho, ham par na ho. do ya teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya. chunanche Madina Munawra se badal chhatney lagey. baain aur daain , hamarey charon taraf doosrey maqamat par barish honey lagi aur hamarey yahan barish yakdam band ho gaee. ye Allah ne logon ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka moa'jza aur apne paighambar (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki karaamat aur dua ki qabooliyat batlaaii."
6094,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''bila shubah sach aadmi ko neki ki taraf bulata hai aur neki jannat ki taraf ley jati hai aur aik shakhs sach boltaa rehta hai yahan tak ke wo siddeeq ka laqab aur martaba hasil kar leta hai aur bila shubah jhoot burai ki taraf ley jata hai aur burai jahannam ki taraf aur aik shakhs jhoot boltaa rehta hai, yahan tak ke wo Allah ke yahan bahut jhoota likh diya jata hai.''"
6095,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''munaafiq ki teen nishaniyan hain, jab boltaa hai jhoot boltaa hai, jab wada karta hai khilaf karta hai aur jab usey ameen banaya jata hai to khayanat karta hai.''"
6096,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''mere paas pichhli raat khuwab mein 2 aadmi aaey unhon-ne kaha ke jisey aap ne dekha ke iska jabdaa chira ja raha tha wo bada hi jhoota tha, jo aik baat ko leta aur saari duniya mein phaila deta tha, qiyamat tak usko yahi saza miltii rahegii.''"
6097,bila shubah sab logon se apni chaal-dhaal aur waza' aur seerat main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sabse zyada mushabeh (similar) Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hain. jab wo apne ghar se bahar nikaltey aur uske baad dobara apne ghar wapas aaney tak unka yahi haal rehta hai lekin jab wo akeley ghar mein rahtey to malum nahi kya kartey rahtey hain.
6098,Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha bila shubah sabse achchha kalam Allah ki kitab hai aur sabse achchha tariqa ( chaal chalan ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tariqa hai.
6099,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii shakhs bhi ya koi cheez bhi takleef bardasht karne waali, jo usey kisi cheez ko sun kar hui ho, Allah se zyada (sabr karne wala) nahi hai. log uske liye aulad thehratey hain aur wo unhein tandurustii deta hai balke unhein rozii bhi deta hai.''"
6100,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (jange-Hunain) mein kuchh maal taqseem kya jaisa ke aap hamesha taqseem kya kartey they. is par qabila Ansar ke aik shakhs ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! us taqseem se Allah ki raza mandi hasil karna maqsud nahi tha. maine kaha ke ye baat main zaroor Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kahoonga. chunanche main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba ke sath tashrif rakhtey they, maine chupkey se ye baat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski ye baat badi na-gawar guzri aur aap ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya aur aap ghussa ho gaey yahan tak ke mere dil mein ye khahish paida hui ke kash! maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko is baat ki khabar na di hoti phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Musa (Alaihissalam) ko is se bhi zyada takleef pahunchai gaee thi lekin unhon-ne sabr kya."
6101,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik kaam kya aur logon ko bhi uski ijazat de di lekin kuchh logon ne iska na karna achchha jaanaa. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski itlaa hui to aap ne khutba diya aur Allah ki hamd ke baad farmaya ke un logon ko kya ho gaya hai jo us kaam se parhez kartey hain, jo main karta hun, Allah ki qism mein Allah ko un sabse zyada janta hun aur un sabse zyada Allah se darney wala hun."
6102,"Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kunwari ladkiyon se bhi zyada sharmeeley they, jab aap koi aisi cheez dekhtey jo aapko na-gawar hoti to ham aap ke chehrey Mubarak se samajh jatey they."
6103,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab koi shakhs apne kisi bhai ko kehta hai ke aey kaafir! to un donon mein se aik kaafir ho gaya aur Ikrima bin Ammar ne Yahya se bayan kya ke unse Abdullaah-bin-Yazeed ne kaha, unhon-ne abu-Salma se suna aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
6104,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis shakhs ne bhi apne kisi bhai ko kaha ke aey kaafir ! to un donon mein se aik kaafir ho gaya. ''
6105,"jisne Islam ke siwa kisi aur mazhab ki jhoot-moot qism khaaii to wo waisaa hi ho jata hai, jiski us ne qism khaaii hai aur jisne kisi cheez se khudkushii kar li to usey jahannam mein usi se azab diya jaeyga aur momin par laanat bhejna usey qatl karne ke barabar hai aur jisne kisi momin par kufr ki tohmat lagai to ye iske qatl ke barabar hai."
6106,"Muaz-bin-Jabal (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey, phir apni qaum mein aatey aur unhein Namaz padhatey . unhon-ne (eik martaba ( Namaz mein sura al-Baqara padhi. is par aik sahib jamat se alag ho gaey aur halki Namaz padhi. jab iske mutaalliq Muaz ko malum hua to kaha wo munafiq hai. Muaz ki ye baat jab unko malum hui to wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham log mehnat ka kaam kartey hain aur apni oontniyon ko khud pani pilaatey hain Muaz ne kal raat hamein Namaz padhai aur sura al-Baqara padhni shuru kar di. isliye main Namaz tod kar alag ho gaya, is par wo kehtey hain ke main munafiq hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Muaaz! tum logon ko fitne mein mubtala kartey ho, teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya (jab imam ho to) sura (iqraa) , Mina ( والشمس وضحاها‏ (aur ( سبح اسم ربك الأعلى‏ ( jaisi soortein padha karo."
6107,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein se jisne laat, uzzaa ki (ya doosrey buton ki) qism khaaii to usey ( لا إله إلا الله) padhna chahiye aur jisne apne sathi se kaha ke aao juwa khelein to usey bataur kaffara sadqa dena chaahiye.''"
6108,"wo umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas pahunchey jo chand sawaaron ke sath they, us waqt umr (Raziallahu anhu) apne walid ki qism kha rahe they. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein pukar kar kaha, khabardaar! yaqinan Allah paak tumhen mana karta hai ke tum apne bap daadon ki qism khaao, to agar kisi ko qism hi khaani hai to Allah ki qism khaaey, warna chup rahe."
6109,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif laey aur ghar mein aik parda latkaa hua tha jis par tasweerein thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya. phir aap ne parda pakda aur usey phaad diya. Ummul-Momenin ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din un logon par sabse zyada azab hoga, jo ye sooratein banatey hain.''"
6110,"aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya main subah ki Namaz jamat se falan imam ki wjah se nahi padhta kyonke wo bahut lambi Namaz padhatey hain. unhon-ne kaha ke us din un imam sahib ko nasihat karne main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maine jitna ghusse mein dekha aisa maine aapko kabhi nahi dekha tha, phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey logo ! tum mein se kuchh log (namaz ba-jamaat padhney se) logon ko door karne waley hain, to jo shakhs bhi logon ko Namaz padhaaey mukhtasar padhaaey, kyonke namaziyon mein koi bimar hota hai koi boodha koi kaam kaaj wala."
6111,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz padh rahe they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid mein qible ki taraf munh ka thook dekha. phir aap ne usey apne hath se saaf kya aur ghussa huey phir farmaya jab tum mein se koi shakhs Namaz mein hota hai Allah Taala iske samney hota hai. isliye koi shakhs Namaz main apne samney na thookey.
6112,"aik sahib ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khoi hui cheez (raaste mein giri padi cheez jisey kisi ne utha liya ho) ke mutaalliq puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya saal bhar logon se poochhtey raho phir iska sar bandhan aur zarf (ظرف) pehchan ke rakh aur kharch kar daal . phir agar iske baad iska Malik aa jaey to wo cheez usey wapas kar de. puchha : ya Rasulullah ! bhuli bhatakii bakri ke mutaalliq kya hukm hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey pakad la kyonke wo tumharey bhai ki hai ya phir bhediye ki hogi. puchha : ya Rasulullah ! aur khoya hua oont ? bayan kya ke is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) naraz ho gaey aur aap ke donon rukhsar surkh ho gaey. ya rawi ne yun kaha ke aap ka chehra surkh ho gaya, phir aap ne farmaya ke tumhen us oont se kya gharaz hai uske sath to uske paon hain aur uska pani hai wo kabhi na kabhi apne Malik ko pa lega."
6113,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ki shakhon ya boriyen (بوریئے) se aik makan chhotey se hujrey ki tarah bana liya tha. wahan aa kar aap tahajjud ki Namaz padha kartey they, chand log bhi wahan aagey aur unhon-ne aap ki iqtida (pairvi) mein Namaz padhi phir sab log dusri raat bhi aagey aur thahrey rahe lekin aap ghar hi mein rahe aur bahar unke paas tashrif nahi laey. log awaz buland karne lagey aur darwazey par kankariyaan maareiin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghussey ki haalat mein bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya tum chahtey ho ke hamesha ye Namaz padhtey raho taake tum par farz ho jaey (us waqt mushkil ho) dekho tum nafl namazein apne gharon mein hi padha karo. kyonke farz namazon ke siwa aadmi ki behtreen nafl Namaz wo hai jo ghar mein padhi jaey."
6114,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''pahlwaan wo nahi hai jo kushtii ladney mein ghalib ho jaey balke aslii pahlwaan to wo hai jo ghussey ki haalat main apne aap par qaabu paaey be qaabu na ho jaaey.''
6115,"2 aadmiyon ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maujoodgii mein jhagdaa kya, ham bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they. aik shakhs doosrey ko ghusse ki haalat mein gali de raha tha aur iska chehra surkh tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main aik aisa kalima janta hun ke agar ye shakhs usey keh ley to uska ghussa door ho jaey. agar ye أعوذ بالله من الشيطان الرجيم keh ley. sahaba ne us se kaha ke suntey nahi, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya farma rahe hain? usne kaha ke kya main deewaanaa hoon?"
6116,aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke mujhey aap koi nasihat farma dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghussa na hua kar. unhon-ne kai martaba ye sawal kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghussa na hua kar.
6117,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''hayaa se hamesha bhalai paida hoti hai."" is par Bashir-bin-kab ne kaha ke hikmat ki kitaabon mein likha hai ke haya se waqaar hasil hota hai, haya se sakeenat hasil hoti hai. Imran ne unse kaha, main tujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis bayan karta hun aur to apni (2 ورقی(do warqi)) kitab ki baatein mujh ko sunata hai."
6118,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka guzar aik shakhs par se hua jo apne bhai par haya ki wjah se naraz ho raha tha aur keh raha tha ke tum bahut sharmaate (شرماتے) ho, maano wo keh raha tha ke tum uski wjah se apna nuqsan kar letey ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke usey chhod do ke haya eman mein se hai."
6119,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) parda mein rehney wali kunwari ladki se bhi zyada haya waley they.
6120,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' agley paighambaron ka kalam jo logon ko mila usmein ye bhi hai ke jab sharm hi na rahi to phir jo ji chahey wo kare.''
6121,"Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah haq baat se haya nahi karta kya aurat ko jab ehtilam ho to is par ghusl wajib hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, agar aurat mani ki tarii dekhey to is par bhi ghusl wajib hai."
6122,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' momin ki misal us sar-sabz darakht ki hai, jiske patey nahi jhadtey. sahaba ne kaha ke ye falan darakht hai, ye falan darakht hai. mere dil mein aaya ke kahun ke ye khajoor ka darakht hai lekin chunkey mein naujawaan tha, isliye mujh ko boltey huey haya aai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai. aur isi sanad se Shoba se riwayat hai ke kaha ham se Khubaib bin Abdur-Rehman ne, unse Hafs bin Aasim ne aur unse ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne isi tarah bayan kya aur ye izafa kya ke phir maine iska zikr umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kya to unhon-ne kaha agar tum ne keh diya hota to mujhey itna itnaa maal milney se bhi zyada khushi hasil hoti."
6123,"aik khatun Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur apne aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nikah ke liye pesh kya aur arz kya : kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mujh se nikah ki zarurat hai? is par Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi boliin, wo kitni be-haya thi. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke wo tum se to achi thin unhon-ne apne aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nikah ke liye pesh kya."
6124,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein (abu-Moosa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) (aur Muaz-bin-Jabal ko (Yaman) bheja to unse farmaya ke (logon ke liye) aasaaniyaan paida karnaa, tangi mein na daalnaa, unhein khushkhabri sanaanaa, Deen se nafrat na dilaanaa aur tum donon aapas mein ittifaq se kaam karnaa, abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ham aisi sar zameen mein ja rahe hain jahan shehad se sharab banai jati hai aur usey (bitaa') kaha jata hai aur jau se sharab banai jati hai aur usey ( مزر‏ ( kaha jata hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har nasha laney wali cheez haram hai."
6125,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aasaanii paida karo, tangi na paida karo, logon ko tasalli aur tashaffii do nafrat na dilaao.''"
6126,"jab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko 2 chizon mein se aik ko ikhtiyar karne ka ikhtiyar diya gaya to aap ne hamesha unmein aasan chizon ko ikhtiyar farmaya, basharte ke usmein gunah ka koi pahlu na hota. agar usmein gunah ka koi pahlu hota to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se sabse zyada door rahtey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni zaat ke liye kisi se badla nahi liya, albatta agar koi shakhs Allah ki hurmat w had ko todtaa to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unse to mahz Allah ki raza mandi ke liye badla letey."
6127,"Ahwaaz naam ke Iraanii Shahar mein ham aik nehar ke kinarey they jo khushk padi thi, phir abu-Barza Aslami sahabi ghodey par tashrif laey aur Namaz padhi aur ghoda chhod diya. ghoda bhaagney laga to aap ne Namaz tod di aur uska peechhaa kya, aakhir uske qareeb pahunchey aur usey pakad liya. phir wapas aa kar Namaz qaza ki, wahan aik shakhs khaarijii tha, wo kehney laga ke us boodhey ko dekho us ne ghodey ke liye Namaz tod daalii. abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz se farigh ho kar aaey aur kaha jab se main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se juda hua hun, kisi ne mujh ko malaamat nahi ki aur unhon-ne kaha ke mera ghar yahan se door hai, agar main Namaz padhta rehta aur ghodey ko bhaagney deta to apne ghar raat tak bhi na pahunch paata aur unhon-ne bayan kya ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat mein rahe hain aur maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aasan Suraton ko ikhtiyar kartey dekha hai."
6128,"aik dehati ne masjid mein peshab kar diya, log uski taraf maarney ko badhey, lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey chhod do aur jahan us ne peshab kya hai us jagah par pani ka aik dol bharaa hua baha do, kyonke tum aasani karne waley bana kar bhejey gaey ho tangi karne waley bana kar nahi bhejey gaey."
6129,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham bachchon se bhi dil lagi kartey, yahan tak ke mere chhotey bhai abu-Umair naam ke se ( mazaaq) farmaatey يا أبا عمير ما amal النغير ''aey abu Umer ! teri nughair naam ke chidiyaa to b-khair hai? ''"
6130,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan ladkiyon ke sath kheltii thi, meri bahut si saheliyaan thin jo mere sath khelaa karti thin, jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif latey to wo chhup jaatiin phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein mere paas bhejtey aur wo mere sath kheltiin."
6131,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik shakhs ne andar aaney ki ijazat chahi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey andar bula lo, ye apni qaum ka bahut hi bura aadmi hai. jab wo shakhs andar aa gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske sath narmii ke sath guftgu farmai. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap ne abhi iske mutaalliq kya farmaya tha aur phir itni narmii ke sath guftgu farmai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Aaisha Allah ke nazdeek martabe ke eitibaar se wo shakhs sabse bura hai jisey log uski bd-khulqi ki wjah se chhod dein."
6132,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hadiye mein deebaa ki chand qubaaein aaein, unmein soney ke batan lagey huey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo qubaaein apne sahaba mein taqseem kar diin aur Makhrima ke liye baqi rakhii, jab Makhrima aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye maine tumharey liye chipa rakhi thi. Ayub ne kaha yani apne kapdey mein chipa rakhi thi aap Makhrima ko khush karne ke liye uske takmey ya ghundii ko dikhla rahe they kyonke wo zara sakht mizaaj aadmi they. is hadis ko Hammad-bin-Zaid ne bhi Ayub ke waaste se riwayat kya Mursalaat main aur Hatim bin wardaan ne kaha ham se Ayub ne bayan kya, unse abi Muleka ne aur unse Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas chand qubaaein tohfe mein aaiin phir aisi hi hadis bayan ki."
6133,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''momin ko aik suraakh se dobara dank nahi lag saktaa.''
6134,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey aur farmaya, kya ye meri khabar sahi hai ke tum raat bhar ibadat kartey rahtey ho aur din mein rozey rakhtey ho? maine kaha ke ji haan ye sahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na karo, ibadat bhi karo aur so bhi, rozey bhi rakho aur bila rozey bhi raho, kyonke tumharey jism ka bhi tum par haq hai, tumhari aankhon ka bhi tum par haq hai, tum se mulaqat ke liye aaney walon ka bhi tum par haq hai, tumhari biwi ka bhi tum par haq hai, ummeed hai ke tumhari umr lambi hogi, tumharey liye yahi kafi hai ke har maheene mein teen rozey rakho, kyonke har neki ka badla das guna milta hai, is tarah zindagi bhar ka roza hoga. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine sakhti chahi to aap ne mere uper sakhti kar di. maine arz kya ke main is se zyada ki taqat rakhta hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir har haftey teen roza rakha kar, bayan kya ke maine aur sakhti chahi aur aap ne mere uper sakhti kar di. maine arz kya ke main us se bhi zyada ki taqat rakhta hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir Allah ke Nabi Dawud (Alaihissalam) jaisa roza rakh. maine poochha, Allah ke Nabi Dawud (Alaihissalam) ka roza kaisa tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik din roza aik din iftaar maano aadhi umr ke rozey ."
6135,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho usey apne mehman ki izzat karni chahiye . uski khaatir daari bas aik din aur raat ki hai mehmani teen din aur raaton ki, iske baad jo ho wo sadqa hai aur mehman ke liye jaaiz nahi ke wo apne mezbaan (میزبان) ke paas itney din thahar jaey ke usey tang kar daaley.''"
6136,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho, is par lazim hai ke apne padosi ko takleef na de, jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho, is par lazim hai ke apne mehman ki izzat karey aur jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho, is par lazim hai ke bhalii baat kahey warna chup rahe.''"
6137,"ham ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap hamein ( tableegh waghaira ke liye) bhejtey hain aur rastey mein ham kuchh qabeelon ke gaaun mein qiyam kartey hain lekin wo hamari mehmani nahi kartey, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka is silsiley mein kya irshad hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par ham se farmaya ke jab tum aisey logon ke paas ja kar utro aur wo jaisa dastoor hai mehmani ke taur par tum ko kuchh dein to usey manzoor kar lo agar na dein to mehmani ka haq qaayde ke muwafiq unse wsool kar lo."
6138,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo shakhs Allah par aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho usey apne mehman ki izzat karni chahiye aur jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho usey chahiye ke wo sila rehmii karey, jo shakhs Allah aur aakhirat ke din par eman rakhta ho, usey chahiye ke achi baat zaban se nikaley warna chup rahe.''"
6139,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Salman Farsi aur abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhaai-bhaai bana diya. aik martaba Salman , abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ki mulaqat ke liye tashrif laey aur umme-Dardaa (Raziallahu anhu) ko badi khasta haalat mein dekha aur poochaa kya haal hai? wo boliin tumharey bhaai abu-Darda ko duniya se koi sarokaar nahi. phir abu-Darda tashrif laey to Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke samney khana pesh kya. unhon-ne kaha ke aap khaaiye , main rozey se hun. Salman Farsi (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke main us waqt tak nahi khaaun ga . jab tak aap bhi na khaaein . chunanche abu-Darda ne bhi khaya raat hui to abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) Namaz padhney ki taiyaarii karne lagey. Salman ne kaha ke so jaaiye , phir jab aakhir raat hui to abu-Darda ne kaha ab uthiye , bayan kya ke phir donon ne Namaz padhi. iske baad Salman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke bila shubah tumharey rab ka tum par haq hai aur tumhari jaan ka bhi tum par haq hai, tumhari biwi ka bhi tum par haq hai, isliyen sarey haq daaron ke huquq ada karo. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur aap se iska zikr kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Salman ne sach kaha hai. abu-Juhaifa ka naam Wahab al-Sawaaii hai, jisey Wahab al-Khair bhi kehtey hain."
6140,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kuchh logon ki mezbaanii ki aur Abdur-Rehman se kaha ke mahmaanon ka poori tarah khayal rakhna kyonke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jaunga, mere aaney se pahley unhein khana khilaa dena. chunanche Abdur-Rehman khana mahmaanon ke paas laey aur kaha ke khana khaaiye. unhon-ne puchha ke hamarey ghar ke Malik kahan hain? unhon-ne arz kya ke aap log khana kha lein. mahmaanon ne kaha ke jab tak hamarey mezbaan (میزبان) na aa jayen ham khana nahi khaaengey. Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke hamari darkhaast qabool kar lijiye kyonke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke aaney tak agar aap log khaney se farigh nahi ho gaey to hamein unki narazgi ka saamnaa hoga. unhon-ne is par bhi inkar kya. main janta tha ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mujh par naraz hongey. isliye jab wo aaey mein unse bachney laga. unhon-ne puchha : tum logon ne kya kya? ghar walon ne unhein bataya to unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ko pukara ! main khamosh raha. phir unhon-ne pukara ! Abdur-Rehman ! main us martaba bhi khamosh raha. phir unhon-ne kaha arey paa-jii main tujh ko qism deta hun ke agar to meri awaz sun raha hai to bahar aa ja , main bahar nikla aur arz kya ke aap apne mahmaanon se poochh lein. mahmaanon ne bhi kaha Abdur-Rehman sach keh raha hai. wo khana hamarey paas laey they. aakhir walid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum logon ne mera intizar kya, Allah ki qism ! main aaj raat khana nahi khaaun-ga . mahmaanon ne bhi qism kha li Allah ki qism jab tak aap na khaaein ham bhi na khaaengey Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha bhai maine aisi kharaab baat kabhi nahi dekhi . mehmaano ! tum log hamari mezbaanii se kyon inkar kartey ho. khair Abdur-Rehman khana la , wo khana laey to aap ne is par apna hath rakh kar kaha, Allah ke naam se shuru karta hun, pehli haalat (khaanaa na khaney ki qasam) shaitan ki taraf se thi. chunanche unhon-ne khana khaya aur unke sath mehmaanon ne bhi khaayaa."
6141,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) apna aik mehman ya kai mehman lekar ghar aaey. phir aap Sham (Syria) hi se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas chaley gaey, jab wo lot kar aaey to meri walida ne kaha ke aaj apne mahmaanon ko chhod kar aap kahan reh gaey they Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne poochaa kya tum ne unko khana nahi khilaaya . unhon-ne kaha ke ham ne to khana unke samney pesh kya lekin unhon-ne inkar kya. ye sun kar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ghussa aaya aur unhon-ne (ghar walon ki) sar-zanish ki aur dukh ka izhar kya aur qism kha li ke main khana nahi khaaun ga . Abdur-Rehman kehtey hain ke main to dar ke maarey chhup gaya to aap ne pukara ke aey paa-jii ! kidhar hai to idhar aa . meri walida ne bhi qism kha li ke agar wo khana nahi khaaengey to wo bhi nahi khaaein gii . iske baad mahmaanon ne bhi qism kha li ke agar Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) nahi khaaengey to wo bhi nahi khaaengey. aakhir Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye ghussa karna shaitaanii kaam tha, phir aap ne khana mangwaya aur khud bhi mahmaanon ke sath khaya (is khaney mein ye barkat hui) jab ye log aik luqma uthatey to nichey se khana aur bhi badh jata tha. Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey bani faraas ki behan ! ye kya ho raha hai, khana to aur badh gaya. unhon-ne kaha ke meri aankhon ki thandak ! ab ye us se bhi zyada ho gaya. jab ham ne khana khaya bhi nahi tha. phir sab ne khaya aur is mein se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja , kehtey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi us khaney mein se khaayaa."
6142,"Abdullah-bin Sehal aur muahaiisa bin Masood khaibar se aaey aur khajoor ke baagh mein aik doosrey se juda ho gaey. Abdullah-bin Sehal wahin qatl kar diye gaey. phir Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal aur Masood ke donon betey huwesa aur muahaiisa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey apne maqtool sathi (Abdullaah (rz)) ke muqaddima mein baat-cheet ki. pahley Abdur-Rehman ne bolnaa chaha jo sabse chhotey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke badey ki badaai karo. (ibne Saeed ne iska maqsad ye) bayan kya ke jo bada hai wo baat-cheet karey, phir unhon-ne apne sathi ke muqaddima mein baat-cheet ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum mein se pachaas (50) aadmi qism kha lein ke Abdullah ko yahudiyon ne maara hai to tum diyat ke mustahiq ho jaogey . unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham ne khud to usey dekha nahi tha (phir iske mutaalliq qism kaisey kha saktey hain?) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir yahood apne pachaas (50) aadmiyon se qism khilwaa kar tum se chhutkara pa lengey. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye kaafir log hain (unki qism ka kya bharosa) chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullah-bin Sehal ke waarison ko diyat khud apni taraf se ada kar di. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke un oonton mein se (jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein diyat mein diye they) aik ontni ko maine pakda wo thaan mein ghus gaee, us ne aik laat mujh ko lagai aur Leis ne kaha mujh se Yahya ne bayan kya, unse Bashir ne aur unse Sehal ne, Yahya ne yahan bayan kya ke main samajhta hun ke Bashir ne (saath mein 'Raafe'-bin-Khadeej) ke alfaz kahey they. aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya, unse Yahya ne bayan kya, unse Bashir ne aur unhon-ne sirf Sehal se riwayat ki."
6143,"Abdullah-bin Sehal aur muahaiisa bin Masood khaibar se aaey aur khajoor ke baagh mein aik doosrey se juda ho gaey. Abdullah-bin Sehal wahin qatl kar diye gaey. phir Abdur-Rehman bin Sehal aur Masood ke donon betey huwesa aur muahaiisa Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey apne maqtool sathi ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu)) ke muqaddima mein guftagu ki. pahley Abdur-Rehman ne bolnaa chaha jo sabse chhotey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke badey ki badaai karo. (ibne Saeed ne iska maqsad ye) bayan kya ke jo bada hai wo guftagu karey, phir unhon-ne apne sathi ke muqaddima mein guftgu ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum mein se pachaas (50) aadmi qism kha lein ke Abdullah ko yahudiyon ne maara hai to tum diyat ke mustahiq ho jaogey . unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham ne khud to usey dekha nahi tha (phir iske mutaalliq qism kaisey kha saktey hain?) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir yahood apne pachaas (50) aadmiyon se qism khilwaa kar tum se chhutkara pa lengey. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye kaafir log hain (unki qism ka kya bharosa) chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullah-bin Sehal ke waarison ko diyat khud apni taraf se ada kar di. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke un oonton mein se (jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein diyat mein diye they) aik ontni ko maine pakda wo thaan mein ghus gaee, us ne aik laat mujh ko lagai aur Leis ne kaha mujh se Yahya ne bayan kya, unse Bashir ne aur unse Sehal ne, Yahya ne yahan bayan kya ke main samajhta hun ke Bashir ne (saath mein 'Raafe'-bin-Khadeej) ke alfaz kahey they. aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne bayan kya, unse Yahya ne bayan kya, unse Bashir ne aur unhon-ne sirf Sehal se riwayat ki."
6144,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey us darakht ka naam bataao , jiski misal musalman ki si hai. wo hamesha apne rab ke hukm se phal deta hai aur uske pat'tey nahi jhadaa kartey. mere dil mein aaya ke keh dun ke wo khajoor ka darakht hai lekin maine keh-naa pasand nahi kya. kyonke majlis mein hazraat Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) jaisey akaabir bhi maujood they. phir jab un donon buzurgon ne kuchh nahi kaha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye khajoor ka darakht hai. jab main apne walid ke sath nikla to maine arz kya ke mere dil mein aaya ke keh dun ye khajoor ka darakht hai, unhon-ne kaha phir tum ne kaha kyon nahi? agar tum ne keh diya hota mere liye itna maal aur asbaab milney se bhi zyada khushi hoti. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke (maine arz kya) sirf is wjah se maine nahi kaha ke jab maine aapko aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) jaisey buzurgon ko khamosh dekha to maine aap buzurgon ke samney baat karna bura jaanaa."
6145,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kuchh she'ron mein daanaaii hoti hai.''
6146,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chal rahe they ke aapko patthar se thokar lagi aur aap gir padey, us se aap ki ungli se khoon bahney laga, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye sher padhaa ''tu too aik ungli hai aur kya hai jo zakhmi ho gaee. . . kya hua agar raahe-maulaa main to zakhmi ho gaii.''"
6147,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ki Shoaraa ke kalam mein se sachcha kalima Labid ka misra'a hai jo ye hai ke Allah ke siwa jo kuchh hai sab ma'doom w fana honey wala hai. Umayya bin abi Salat shaair to qareeb tha ke musalman ho jaey.
6148,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang khaibar mein gaey aur ham ne raat main safar kya, itney mein musalmanon ke aadmi ne Aamir bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke apne kuchh sher ashaar sunao. rawi ne bayan kya ke Aamir shaair they. wo logon ko apni hudi sunaney lagey. ''aey Allah ! agar to na hota to ham hidayat na patey na ham sadqa de saktey aur na Namaz padh saktey. ham tujh par fidaa hon, ham ne jo kuchh pahley gunah kiye unko to maaf kar de aur jab (dushman se) hamara saamnaa ho to hamein Sabit qadam rakh aur ham par sukoon nazil farmaa. jab hamein jang ke liye bulaya jata hai, to ham maujood ho jatey hain aur dushman ne bhi pukar kar ham se nijat chahi hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye kon oonton ko haank raha hai jo hudi (oonton ko hankaaney ke liye gaaya janey wala geet) ga raha hai? sahaba ne arz kya ke Aamir bin Akwaa hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah paak is par raham kare. aik sahabi yani umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ab to Aamir Shahid huey. kash! aur chand roz aap ham ko Aamir se fayda uthaney detey. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir ham khaibar aaey aur usko gher liya us ghiraao mein ham shadeed faaqon mein mubtala huey, phir Allah Taala ne khaibar walon par ham ko fateh ata farmai jis din un par fateh hui uski Sham ko logon ne jagah-jagah aag jalaaii. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke ye aag kaisi hai, kis kaam ke liye tum logon ne ye aag jalaaii hai? sahaba ne arz kya ke gosht pakaaney ke liye. is par aap ne malum farmaya kis cheez ke gosht ke liye? sahaba ne kaha ke basti ke paaltu gadhon ka gosht pakaaney ke liye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke gosht ko bartanon mein se phenk do aur bartanon ko tod do. aik sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ham gosht to phenk dein, magar bartan todney ke bajaey agar dho lein? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya achchha yun hi kar lo. jab logon ne jang ki saf bandi kar li to Aamir ( ibne- Akwaa shaair ( ne apni talwaar se aik Yahudi par waar kya, unki talwaar chhoti thi uski nauk palat kar khud unke ghutnon par lagi aur uski wjah se unki shahadat ho gaee. jab log wapas aaney lagey to Salma ( Aamir ke bhai ( ne bayan kya ke mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke mere chehrey ka rang badla hua hai. malum farmaya ke kya baat hai? maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! par mere maan aur bap fidaa hon, log keh rahe hain ke Aamir ke aamaal barbad ho gaey. (kyonke unki maut khud unki talwaar se hui hai) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye kis ne kahaa? maine arz kya : fulaan, fulaan, falan aur Usaid-bin-Huzair Ansari ne. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne ye baat kahi us ne jhoot kaha hai unhein to dohra ajr milega. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni 2 ungliyon ko mila kar ishara kya ke wo aabid bhi tha aur Mujahid bhi (to ibadat aur jihad donon ka sawab us ne paya ( Aamir ki tarah to bahut kam bahaadur Arab mein paida huey hain (wo aisa bahaadur aur nek aadmi tha) ."
6149,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (eik safar ke mauqe par) apni aurton ke paas aaey jo oonton par Sawar ja rahi thin, unke sath Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) Anas ki walida bhi thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke afsos , anjasha ! sheeshon ko aahisatagi se ley chal . abu-Qilaba ne kaha ke Nabi Karim ne aurton se mutaalliq aisey alfaz ka istemal farmaya ke agar tum mein koi shakhs istemal karey to tum is par aib joii karo. yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye irshad ke sheeshon ko narmii se ley chal."
6150,"Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne mushrekeen ki hijo karne ki ijazat chahi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unka aur mera khandan to aik hi hai (phir to main bhi us hijo mein Sharik ho jaaunga). Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main hijo se aapko is tarah saaf nikal doonga jis tarah gundhey huey aatey se baal nikal liya jata hai. aur Hisham-bin-Urwa se riwayat hai, unse unke walid ne bayan kya ke main Hassaan-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ko Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki majlis mein bura kehney laga to unhon-ne kaha ke Hassan ko bura bhala na kaho, wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf se mushrikon ko jawab deta tha."
6151,"unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo halaat aur qisson ke tehet Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tazkira kar rahe they. ke aik baar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumharey aik bhai ne koi buri baat nahi kahi . aap ka ishara ibne- Rawaha ki taraf tha (apne ashaar mein) unhon-ne yun kaha tha ''aur ham mein Allah ke rasool hain jo uski kitab ki tilawat kartey hain, us waqt jab fajr ki roshni phoot kar phail jati hai. hamein unhon-ne gumrahi ke baad hidayat ka rasta dikhaayaa. to hamarey dil is baat par yaqin rakhtey hain ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo kuchh farmaya wo zaroor waaqe hoga. aap raat is tarah guzaarey hain ke unka pahlu bistar se juda rehta hai (yani jaag kar) jabke kaafiron ke bojh se unki khuwab gaahein bojhal hui rehti hain.'' Yunus ke sath us hadis ko Aqeel ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya aur Muhammad-bin Waleed Zubaidi ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se us hadis ko riwayat kya."
6152,"aey abu-Huraira! mein aapko Allah ki qism de kar poochhta hun, kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Hassan! Allah ke rasool ki taraf se mushrikon ko jawab do, aey Allaah! roohul-qudus ke zariey unki madad kar. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke haan."
6153,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hassan (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya unki hijo karo (yani mushrekeen Quraish ki). ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( هاجهم (ke alfaz farmaai ( Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) terey sath hain.
6154,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar tum mein se koi shakhs apna pet peep se bharey to ye us se behtar hai ke wo usey sher se bharey.''
6155,maine Abu-Saleh se suna aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se farmaya ''agar tum mein se koi shakhs apna pet peep se bhar ley to ye us se behtar hai ke wo she'ron se bhar jaaey.''
6156,"abu-Qaees ke bhai Aflah (mere dudh-sharik chacha ne) mujh se parde ka hukm nazil honey ke baad andar aaney ki ijazat chaahii, maine kaha ke Allah ki qism jab tak Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ijazat na dengey mein andar aaney ki ijazat nahi doongii. kyonke abu-Qaees ke bhai ne mujhey doodh nahi pilaya balke abu-Qaees ki biwi ne doodh pilaya hai. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mard ne to mujhey doodh nahi pilaya tha, doodh to unki biwi ne pilaya tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhein andar aaney ki ijazat de do, kyonke wo tumharey chacha hain, tumharey hath mein mitti lagey. Urwa ne kaha ke usi wjah se Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti thin ke jitney rishtey khoon ki wjah se haram hotey hain wo doodh pilaaney se bhi haram hi samjho ."
6157,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Haj se) waapsii ka irada kya to dekha ke Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) apne khemey ke darwaza par ranjeeda khadi hain kyonke wo haaiza ho gaee thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ( عقرى حلقى ( (ye Quraish ka muhaawara hai) ab tum hamein rokogii! phir malum farmaya kya tum ne qurbani ke din tawaaf ifaaza kar liya tha? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan, farmaya ke phir chalo."
6158,"fateh Makka ke mauqe par main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. maine dekha ke aap ghusl kar rahe hain aur aap ki sahibzadi Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne parda kar diya hai. maine salam kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum kya ke ye kon hain? maine kaha ke Umme-Hani binte-abi-Talib hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Umme-Hani ! marhaba ho. jab aap ghusl kar chukey to khadey ho kar aath (8) rakaat padhin. aap us waqt aik kapdey mein jism Mubarak ko lapetey huey they. jab Namaz se farigh ho gaey to maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere bhai ( Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu)) ka khayal hai ke wo aik aisey shakhs ko qatl karengey jisey maine aman de rakhi hai. yani falan bin Hubaira ko . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Umme-Hani jisey tum ne aman di usey ham ne bhi aman di. Umme-Hani ne bayan kya ke ye Namaz chasht ki thi."
6159,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko dekha ke qurbani ke liye aik ontni haankey liye ja raha hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is par Sawar ho kar jaa, unhon-ne kaha ke ye to qurbani ka janwar hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Sawar ho jaa, afsos ( ويلك (dusri ya teesri martaba ye farmaayaa."
6160,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ko dekha ke qurbani ka oont hankaaey ja raha hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se kaha ke to is par Sawar ho jaa. us ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ye to qurbani ka oont hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dusri baar ya teesri baar farmaya ke teri kharabi ho, to Sawar ho jaa."
6161,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein they aur aap ke sath aap ka aik habshi ghulam tha. unka naam anjasha tha wo hudi (oonton ko tez chalaney ka geet) padh raha tha (jiski wjah se sawari tez chalney lagii). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''afsos ( ويحك (aey anjasha ! sheeshon ke sath ahista-ahista chal."""
6162,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aik shakhs ne doosrey shakhs ki tareef ki. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya afsos ( ويلك ( tum ne apne bhai ki gardan kaat di, teen martaba (ye farmaya ( agar tumhen kisi ki tareef hi karni pad jaey to ye kaho ke falan ke mutaalliq mera ye khayal hai. agar wo baat iske mutaalliq janta ho aur Allah iska nigraan hai main to Allah ke muqaabley mein kisi ko nek nahi keh sakta yani yun nahi keh sakta ke wo Allah ke ilm mein bhi nek hai."
6163,"aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuchh taqseem kar rahe they. bani Tameem ke aik shakhs zul-khuwesraa ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! insaf se kaam lijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, afsos ! agar main hi insaf nahi karunga to phir kon karega . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! mujhey ijazat dein to main uski gardan mar dun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. iske kuchh ( qabeele waale) aisey log paida hongey ke tum unki Namaz ke muqable main apni Namaz ko maamooli samjhogey aur unke rozon ke muqable main apne rozey ko maamooli samjhogey lekin wo Deen se is tarah nikal chukey hongey jis tarah teer shikar se nikal jata hai. teer ke phal mein dekha jaey to is par bhi koi nishan nahi milega. uski lakdi par dekha jaey to is par bhi koi nishan nahi milega. phir uske dandaanon mein dekha jaey aur is mein bhi kuchh nahi milega phir uske par main dekha jaey to usmein bhi kuchh nahi milega. (yani shikar ke jism ko paar karne ka koi nishaan) teer leed aur khoon ko paar karke nikal chuka hoga. ye log us waqt paida hongey jab logon mein phoot pad jaeygi. (eik khaleefa par muttafiq na hongey) unki nishani unka aik mard (sardaar lashakr) hoga. jiska aik hath aurat ke pistaan ki tarah hoga ya (farmaayaa) gosht ke lothdey ki tarah thul-thul hil raha hoga. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis suni aur main gawahi deta hun ke main Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha. jab unhon-ne un khaarijiyon se ( naharwaan mein) jang ki thi. maqtooleen mein talash ki gaee to aik shakhs unhiin sifaat ka laya gaya jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bayan ki thin. iska aik hath pistaan ki tarah ka tha."
6164,"aik sahabi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main to tabah ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, afsos (kya baat huii?) unhon-ne kaha ke maine Ramazan main apni biwi se sohbat kar li. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir aik ghulam aazad kar. unhon-ne arz kya ke mere paas ghulam hai hi nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir 2 mahiney mutwaatir rozey rakh. usne kaha ke uski mujh mein taqat nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir sath miskinon ko khana khilaa. kaha ke itna bhi main apne paas nahi paata . iske baad khajoor ka aik tokraa aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey ley aur sadqa kar de. unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya apne ghar walon ke siwa kisi aur ko? us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! sarey Madeene ke donon tanaabon yani donon kinaron mein mujh se zyada koi mohtaaj nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par itna hans diye ke aap ke aagey ke daant dikhai dene lagey. farmaya ke jao tum hi ley lo. Auzaaee ke sath is hadis ko Yunus ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya aur Abdur-Rehman bin Khalid ne Zohri se is hadis mein bajaey lafz ( ويحك (ke lafz ( ويلك‏ . Mina ( riwayat kya hai) mana donon ke aik hi hain) ."
6165,"aik dehati ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! hijrat ke barey mein mujhey kuchh bataiye (uskii niyat hijrat ki thi). Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tujh par afsos! hijrat ko to ney kya samjha hai ye bahut mushkil hai. tumharey paas kuchh oont hain. unhon-ne arz kya ke ji haan, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya kya tum unki zakat ada kartey ho? unhon-ne arz kya ke ji haan, farmaya ke phir saat (7) samandar paar amal kartey raho. Allah tumharey kisi amal ke sawab ko zaaye na karega."
6166,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, afsos ( ويلكم (ya ( ويحكم ( Shoba ne bayan kya ke shak unke Shekh (Waaqid bin-Muhammad ko) tha. mere baad tum kaafir na ho jana ke aik doosrey ki gardan maarney lago aur nazar ne Shoba se bayan kya ( ويحكم (aur Umar-bin Muhammad ne apne walid se ( ويلكم (ya ( ويحكم (ke lafz naql kiye hain."
6167,"aik badwi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur puchha : ya Rasulullah ! qiyamat Kab aaeygi? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, afsos ( ويلك ( tum ne us qiyamat ke liye kya taiyaarii kar li hai? unhon-ne arz kya maine uske liye to koi taiyaarii nahi ki hai albatta main Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir tum qiyamat ke din unke sath ho, jis se tum mohabbat rakhtey ho. ham ne arz kya aur hamarey sath bhi yahi mamla hoga? farmaya ke haan. ham us din bahut zyada khush huey, phir Mughira ke aik ghulam wahan se guzrey wo mere ham-umr they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ye bachcha zinda raha to iska budhapa aaney se pahley qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi."
6168,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' insan uske sath hai jis se wo mohabbat rakhta hai.''
6169,"aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ka us shakhs ke barey mein kya irshad hai jo aik jamat se mohabbat rakhta hai lekin unse mail nahi ho saka hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke insan uske sath hai jis se wo mohabbat rakhta hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Jareer-bin-Haazim, Sulaimaan-bin-Qarm aur abu-Awana ne Aamash se ki, unse abu-Waeil ne, unse Abdullah-bin-Masood ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
6170,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya gaya aik shakhs aik jamat se mohabbat rakhta hai lekin us se mil nahi saka hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke insan uske sath hai jis se wo mohabbat rakhta hai. Sufiyan ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) abu-Muawia aur Muhammad-bin Ubaid ne ki hai.
6171,"aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : ya Rasulullah ! qiyamat Kab qaaim hogii? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tum ne uske liye kya taiyaarii ki hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke maine uske liye bahut saari namaazein, rozey aur sadqey nahi taiyaar kar rakhey hain, lekin main Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum uske sath ho jis se tum mohabbat rakhtey ho."
6172,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne-Sayyaad se farmaya ''maine us waqt apne dil mein aik baat chipa rakhi hai, wo kya hai? ''wo bola ( الدخ‏ . Mina ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya chal door ho jaa."""
6173,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ibne-Sayyaad ki taraf gaey. bahut se doosrey sahaba bhi sath they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke wo chand bachchon ke sath bani maghaala ke qile ke paas khel raha hai. un dinon ibne-Sayyaad buloogh ke qareeb tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aamad ka usey ehsas nahi hua. yahan tak ke aap ne uski peeth par apna hath maara . phir farmaya kya to gawahi deta hai ke main Allah ka rasool hoon? us ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekh kar kaha, mein gawahi deta hun ke aap ummiyon ke yani ( Arbon ke) rasool hain. phir ibne-Sayyaad ne kaha kya aap gawahi detey hain ke main Allah ka rasool hoon? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par usey dafa' kar diya aur farmaya, mein Allah aur uske rasool par eman laya. phir ibne-Sayyaad se aap ne poochha, tum kya dekhtey ho? usne kaha ke mere paas sachcha aur jhoota donon aatey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumharey liye maamle ko mushtabah kar diya gaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tumharey liye aik baat apne dil mein chipa rakhi hai? usne kaha ke wo ( الدخ‏ ( hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke door ho, apni haisiyat se aagey na badh . umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap mujhey ijazat dengey ke usey qatl kar dun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar ye wahi ( dajjal ( hai to is par ghalib nahi hua ja sakta aur agar ye dajjal nahi hai to usey qatl karne mein koi khair nahi."
6174,iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ubai-bin-Kab Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar us khajoor ke baagh ki taraf rawaana huey jahan ibne-Sayyaad rehta tha. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baagh mein pahunchey to aap ne khajoor ki tahniyon mein chhipnaa shuru kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chahtey they ke us se pahley ke wo dekhey chhup kar kisi bahaney ibne-Sayyaad ki koi baat sunein. ibne-Sayyaad aik makhmalii chadar ke bistar par leta hua tha aur kuchh gungunaa raha tha. ibne-Sayyaad ki maan ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khajoor ke tanon se chhup kar aatey huey dekh liya aur usey bata diya ke aey saaf! (ye iska naam tha) Muhammad aa rahe hain. chunanche wo mutanabbeh ho gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar uski maan usey mutanabbeh na karti to baat saaf ho jati.
6175,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ke majma' mein khadey huey aur Allah ki uski shaan ke mutabiq tareef karne ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dajjal ka zikr kya aur farmaya ke main tumhen us se daraataa hun. koi Nabi aisa nahi guzra jisne apni qaum ko us se na daraayaa ho. Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne apni qaum ko us se daraayaa lekin main uski tumhen aik aisi nishani bataunga jo kisi Nabi ne apni qaum ko nahi batai tum jantey ho ke wo kaana hoga aur Allah kaana nahi hai.
6176,"jab qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke marhaba un logon ko jo aan pahunchey to na wo zaleel huey, na sharminda (khushii se musalman ho gaey warna maarey jatey sharminda hotey ( unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! ham qabila Rabe ki shaakh se talluq rakhtey hain aur chunkey hamarey aur aap ke darmyan qabila muzar ke kaafir log rukawat hain isliye ham aap ki khidmat mein sirf hurmat waley mahinon hi mein hazir ho saktey hain (jin mein loot-khasot nahi hoti (aap kuchh aisi jachii-tulii baat bata dein jis par amal karne se ham jannat mein dakhil ho jayen aur jo log nahi aa sakey hain unhein bhi uski dawat pahunchaaein . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke char chaar cheezein hain. Namaz qaaim karo, zakat do, Ramazan ke rozey rakho aur ghaneemat ka panchwan hissey ( baitul-maal ko) ada karo aur dabbaa, hantam, naqeer aur muzaffat mein na piyo."
6177,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ahad todney waley ke liye qiyamat mein aik jhanda uthaya jaeyga aur pukar diya jaeyga ke ye falan bin falan ki daghaa bazi ka nishan hai.''
6178,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ahad todney waley ke liye qiyamat mein aik jhanda uthaya jaeyga aur pukara jaeyga ke ye falan bin falan ki daghaa bazi ka nishan hai.''
6179,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein koi shakhs ye na kahey ke mera nafs paleed ho gaya hai balke ye kahey ke mera dil kharaab ya pareshan ho gaya. ''
6180,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mein se koi hargiz yun na kahey ke mera nafs paleed ho gaya lekin yun keh sakta hai ke mera dil kharaab ya pareshan ho gaya. ''is hadis ko Aqeel ne bhi ibne-Shahab se riwayat kya hai."""
6181,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah taala farmata hai ke insan zamana ko gali deta hai halanke main hi zamana hun, mere hi hath mein raat aur din hain.''"
6182,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''angoor (inab) ko (karam) na kaho aur ye na kaho ke haaye zamana ki naamuraadii. kyonke zamana to Allah hi ke ikhtiyar mein hai.''
6183,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''log (angoor ko) ( karam ( kehtey hain, ( karam ( to momin ka dil hai.''"
6184,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kisi ke liye apne aapko qurbaan karne ka lafz kehtey nahi suna, siwa Sad-bin-abi-Waqas ke. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they. teer mar , aey Sad ! mere maan-baap tum par qurbaan hon, mera khayal hai ke ye Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par farmaya,"
6185,"wo aur abu-Talha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (Madina Munawra ke liye) rawaana huey. Ummul-Momenin Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari par aap ke peechhey thin, raaste mein kisi jagah ontni ka paon phisal gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Ummul-Momenin gir gaey. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mera khayal hai abu-Talha ne apni sawari se fauran apne ko gira diya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunch gaey aur arz kya : ya Nabi Allah ! Allah aap par mujhey qurbaan karey kya aapko koi chot aai ? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, albatta aurat ko dekho . chunanche abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kapda apne chehrey par daal liya, phir Ummul-Momenin ki taraf badhey aur apna kapda unke uper daal diya. iske baad wo khadi ho gain aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Ummul-Momenin ke liye abu-Talha ne paalaan mazbut baandhaa. ab aap ne Sawar ho kar phir safar shuru kya, jab Madina Munawra ke qareeb pahunchey (ya yun kaha ke Madina dikhai dene laga ( to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ham lotney waley hain tauba kartey huey apne rab ki ibadat kartey huey aur uski hamd bayan kartey huey.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey barabar kehtey rahe yahan tak ke Madina mein dakhil ho gaey."
6186,"ham mein se aik sahib ke yahan bachcha paida hua to unhon-ne iska naam Qasim rakha. ham ne unse kaha ke ham tum ko abul-Qaasim keh kar nahi pukaarengey (kyonke abul-Qaasim Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kunniyat thi) aur na ham tumhari izzat ke liye aisa karengey. un sahib ne uski khabar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di, to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne betey ka naam Abdur-Rehman rakh ley."
6187,ham mein se aik shakhs ke yahan bachcha paida hua to unhon-ne iska naam Qasim rakha. sahaba ne unse kaha ke jab tak ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se na poochh lein. ham us naam par tumhari kunniyat nahi honey dengey. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mere naam par naam rakho lekin meri kunniyat na ikhtiyar karo.
6188,abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' mere naam par naam rakho lekin meri kunniyat na rakho .''
6189,ham mein se aik aadmi ke yahan bachcha paida hua to unhon-ne uska naam Qasim rakha. sahaba ne kaha ke ham tumhari kunniyat abul-Qaasim nahi rakhengey aur na teri aankh us kunniyat se pukar kar thandii karengey. wo shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se iska zikr kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne ladkey ka naam Abdur-Rehman rakh lo.
6190,"unke walid (huzn bin abi wahab) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumhara naam kya hai? unhon-ne bataya ke) huzn ( ) ba-maanaa sakhti ( . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum ( سهل ( ) ba-maanaa narmii ( ho, phir unhon-ne kaha ke mera naam mere walid rakh gaey hain usey mein nahi badloon ga . ibne-Musaiyab (Rahmatullahi-alaih) bayan kartey they ke chunanche hamarey khandan mein baad tak hamesha sakhti aur museebat ka daur raha."
6191,"munzir bin abi Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ki wilaadat hui to unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya gaya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachcha ko apni raan par rakh liya. abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) baithey huey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi cheez mein jo samney thi masroof ho gaey (aur bachcha ki taraf tawajjoh hat gai) . abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne bachcha ke mutaalliq hukm diya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan se utha liya gaya. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mutwajjeh huey to farmaya ke bachcha kahan hai? abu-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham ne usey ghar bhej diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : iska naam kya hai? arz kya ke fulaan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, balke iska naam munzir hai. chunanche isi din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka yahi naam munzir rakha."
6192,"Ummul-Momenin Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ka naam barra tha, kaha janey laga ke wo apni paakii zahir karti hain. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka naam Zenab rakha."
6193,"main Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ke paas betha hua tha to unhon-ne mujh se bayan kya ke unke dada huzn Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumhara naam kya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mera naam huzn hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum Sehal ho, unhon-ne kaha ke main to apne bap ka rakha hua naam nahi badloonga. Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne kaha iske baad se ab tak hamarey khandan mein sakhti aur museebat hi rahi. ( حزونة ( se suoobat murad hai."
6194,maine ibne-abii-Aufii se poochha. tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahibzadey Ibrahim ko dekha tha? bayan kya ke unki wafat bachpan hi mein ho gaee thi aur agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad kisi Nabi ki aamad hoti to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahibzadey zinda rahtey lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad koi Nabi nahi aayega .
6195,jab aap ke farzand Ibrahim ka intiqal hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' uske liye jannat mein aik doodh pilaaney wali daaya muqarrar ho gaee hai.''
6196,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' mere naam par naam rakho, lekin meri kunniyat na ikhtiyar karo kyonke main Qasim ( taqseem karne wala ( hun aur tumharey darmyan (deen ke ilm ko) taqseem karta hoon.'' aur is riwayat ko Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se naql kya."
6197,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''tum mere naam par naam rakho lekin tum meri kunniyat na ikhtiyar karo aur jisne mujhey khuwab mein dekha to usne mujhey hi dekha kyonke shaitan meri sura mein nahi aa sakta aur jisne qasdan meri taraf koi jhooti baat mansub ki us ne apna thikana jahannam mein bana liyaa.''
6198,mere yahan aik bachcha paida hua to main usey lekar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iska naam Ibrahim rakha aur aik khajoor apne munh mein narm karke iske munh mein dali aur uske liye barkat ki dua ki phir usey mujhey de diya. ye abu-Musa ki badi aulad thi.
6199,jis din Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat hui us din suraj girahan hua tha. usko Abu-Bakra ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya hai.
6200,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sar Mubarak rukoo se uthaya to ye dua ki اللهم أنج الوليد بن الوليد وسلمة بن هشام ، Mina وعياش بن أبي ربيعة ، Mina والمستضعفين بمكة ''aey Allah ! Waleed bin Waleed, Salma bin Hishaam, Ayash bin abi Rabee aur Makka mein doosrey maujood kamzor musalmanon ko nijat de-dey. '' اللهم اشدد وطأتك على مضر ، Mina اللهم اجعلها عليهم سنين كسني يوسف ''aey Allah ! qabila Muzar ke kaafiron ko sakht pakad, aey Allah ! un par Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane jaisa qahat nazil farmaa. ''"
6201,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Aaisha! ye Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) hain aur tumhen salam kehtey hain.'' maine kaha aur un par bhi salam aur Allah ki rehmat ho. bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wo cheezein dekhtey they jo ham nahi dekhtey they.
6202,Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) musaafiron ke saman ke sath thin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghulam anjasha aurton ke oont ko haank rahe they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''anjash! zara is tarah aahisatagi se ley chal jaisey sheeshon ko lekar jata hai.''
6203,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) husne-akhlaaq mein sab logon se badh kar they, mera aik bhai abu-umair naam ke tha. bayan kya ke mera khayal hai ke bachche ka doodh chhoot chuka tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab tashrif latey to us se mazaaq mein farmatey ""aey Umer tumhaara nughair naami parinda kahan hai?"" aksar aisa hota ke Namaz ka waqt ho jata aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey ghar mein hotey . aap us bistar ko bichhaaney ka hukm detey jis par aap baithey huey hotey , chunanche usey jhaad kar is par pani chhidak diya jata. phir aap khadey hotey aur ham aap ke peechhey khadey hotey aur aap hamein Namaz padhaatey."
6204,Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko unki kunniyat abu-Turaab sabse zyada pyari thi aur is kunniyat se unhein pukara jata to bahut khush hotey they kyonke ye kunniyat abu-Turaab khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne rakhi thi. aik din Fatima (Raziallahu anha) se khafa ho kar wo bahar chaley aaey aur masjid ki diwar ke paas let gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke peechhey aaey aur farmaya ke ye to diwar ke paas letey huey hain. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki peeth mitti se bhar chuki thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki peeth se mitti jhaadtey huey ( piyaar se) farmaney lagey abu-Turaab uth jao .
6205,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat ke din Allah ke nazdeek sabse badtareen naam uska hoga jo apna naam shahanshaah rakhey.''
6206,Allah ke nazdeek sabse badtareen naam aur kabhi Sufiyan ne aik se zyada martaba ye riwayat is tarah bayan ki ke Allah ke nazdeek sabse badtareen naamon (jama ke seeghey ke saath) mein uska naam hoga jo ''shahanshaah'' apna naam rakhega. Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke abu-Zinaad ke ghair ne kaha ke iska mafhoom hai'' shaahaan Shah '' .
6207,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik gadhey par Sawar huey jis par fidak ka bana hua aik kapda bichhaa hua tha, Usama aap ke peechhey sawar they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bani Haris bin khazraj mein Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley ja rahe they, ye waqia jange-badr se pahley ka hai ye donon rawaana huey aur rastey mein aik majlis se guzrey jis mein Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool bhi tha. Abdullah ne abhi tak apne Islam ka elaan nahi kya tha. us majlis mein kuchh musalman bhi they. buton ki parastish karne waley kuchh mushrekeen bhi they aur kuchh Yahudi bhi they. musalman shurakaa mein Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha bhi they. jab majlis par (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) sawari ka ghubaar ud kar padaa to Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne apni chadar naak par rakh li aur kehney laga ke ham par ghubaar na udaao, iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (qareeb pahunchne ke baad) unhein salam kya aur khadey ho gaey. phir sawari se utar kar unhein Allah ki taraf bulaya aur Quran Majeed ki aayatein unhein padh kar sunaiin. is par Abdullah-bin-Ubai ibne-Salool ne kaha ke bhaley aadmi jo kalam tum ne padha us se behtar kalam nahi ho sakta. agarche waqei ye haq hai magar hamari majlison mein aa kar uski wjah se hamein takleef na diya karo. jo tumharey paas jaey bas usko ye qissey suna diya karo. Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : zaroor, ya Rasulullah ! aap hamari majlison mein bhi tashrif laya karein kyonke ham usey pasand kartey hain. us maamle par muslmaanon, mushrikon aur yahudiyon ka jhagdaa ho gaya aur qareeb tha ke aik doosrey ke khilaf hath utha dein. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein khamosh kartey rahe aakhir jab sab log khamosh ho gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par baithey aur rawaana huey. jab Sad-bin-Ubada ke yahan pahunchey to unse farmaya ke aey Sad! tum ne nahi suna aaj abu-Hubaab ne kis tarah baatein ki hain. aap ka ishara Abdullah-bin-Ubai ki taraf tha ke usne ye baatein kahi hain Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) boley, mera bap aap par qurbaan ho, ya Rasulullah! aap usey maaf farma dein aur us se darguzar farmaaein, us zaat ki qism jisne aap par kitab nazil ki hai Allah ne aapko sachcha kalam de kar yahan bheja jo aap par utara . aap ke tashrif laney se pahley us Shahar (Madina munawwara) ke baashindey is par muttafiq ho gaey they ke usey (Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii ko) shahi taaj pehna dein aur shahi amama baandh dein lekin Allah ne sachcha kalam de kar aapko yahan bhej diya aur ye tajwiz moquf rahi to wo uski wjah se chid gaya aur jo kuchh aap ne aaj mulaahaza kya, wo usi jalan ki wjah se hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai ko maaf kar diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaaba, mushrekeen aur ahle-kitab se jaisa ke unhein Allah Taala ne hukm diya tha. darguzar kya kartey they aur unki taraf se pahunchne wali takleefon par sabr kya kartey they. Allah Taala ne bhi irshad farmaya hai ke ''tum un logon se jinhein kitab di gaee hai (azeeyat deh baatein) sunogey.'' doosrey mauqe par irshad farmaya ''bahut se ahle-kitab khahish rakhtey hain.'' chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein maaf karne ke liye Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq taujeeh kya kartey they. bil-aakhir aapko ( jang ki) ijazat di gaee. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-badr kya aur Allah ke hukm se usmein kuffaar ke badey badey bahaadur aur Quraish ke sardaar qatl kiye gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba ke sath fateh mand aur ghaneemat ka maal liye huey wapas huey, unke sath kuffaare-Quraish ke kitney hi bahaadur sardaar qaid bhi karke laey to us waqt Abdullaah-bin-Ubaii-bin-salool aur uske but-parast mushrik sathi kehney lagey ke ab unka kaam jam gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait kar lo, us waqt unhon-ne Islam par bait ki aur bazahir musalman ho gaey (magar dil mein nifaq rahaa)."
6208,"unhon-ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! aap ne janab abu-Taalib ko unki wafat ke baad koi fayda pahunchaayaa, wo aap ki hifazat kya kartey they aur aap ke liye logon par ghussa hua kartey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, wo dozakh mein us jagah par hain jahan takhnon tak aag hai agar main na hota to wo dozakh ke nichey ke tabqey mein rehtey."
6209,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein they, raaste mein hudi (padhneywaaley ne) hudi padhi to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey anjasha! sheeshon ko ahista-ahista lekar chal, tujh par afsos.''"
6210,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein they, anjasha naam ke ghulam aurton ki sawaariyon ko qurbani ka janwar padhta lekar chal raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ''anjasha! sheeshon ko aahista ley chal.'' abu-Qilaba ne bayan kya ke murad auratein thin."
6211,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik hudi padhney waaley they anjasha naam ke unki awaz badi achi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ''anjasha! aahista chaal ikhtiyar kar, un sheeshon ko mat tod.'' Qatada ne bayan kya ke murad kamzor auratein thin (ke sawari se gir na jaaein)."
6212,"Madina Munawra par (eik raat naa-maaloom awaz ki wjah se) dar taarii ho gaya. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abu-Talha ke aik ghodey par Sawar huey. phir (waapas aa kar) farmaya ''hamein to koi ( khof ki) cheez nazar na aaii, albatta ye ghoda to maano dariya tha.''"
6213,"kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaahinon ke barey mein poochha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke unki (pesheen goiyon ki) koi haisiyat nahi. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! lekin wo kabhi-kabhi aisi baatein kartey hain jo sahi Sabit hoti hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo baat, sachchii baat hoti hai jisey jin farishton se sun kar uda leta hai aur phir usey apne wali (kaahin) ke kaan mein murgh ki awaz ki tarah daalta hai. iske baad kaahin us (eik sachchii baat) mein so se zyada jhoot mila detey hain."
6214,"mujhey Jabir-bin-Abdullah ne khabar di, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir mere paas wahi aaney ka silsile band ho gaya. aik din mein chal raha tha ke maine aasman ki taraf se aik awaz suni, maine aasman ki taraf nazar uthai to maine phir us farishta ko dekha jo mere paas ghare-hira mein aaya tha, wo aasman w zameen ke darmyan kursi par betha hua tha."
6215,"maine aik raat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) (khaala) ke ghar guzaarii, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi us raat wahin thahrey huey they. jab raat ka aakhiri tehai hissey hua ya uska kuchh hissey reh gaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uth baithey aur aasman ki taraf dekha phir is aayat ki tilawat ki إن في خلق السموات والأرض واختلاف الليل والنهار لآيات لأولي الألباب‏ ''bila shubah aasman ki aur zameen ki paidaaish main aur din raat ke badaltey rehney mein aql walon ke liye nishaniyan hain.''"
6216,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina ke baaghon mein se aik baagh mein they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein aik lakdi thi, aap usko pani aur keechad mein mar rahe they. us doran mein aik sahib ne baagh ka darwaza khulwaanaa chaha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke uske liye darwaza khol de aur unhein jannat ki khushkhabri suna de. main gaya to wahan Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) maujood they, maine unke liye darwaza khola aur unhein jannat ki khushkhabri sunai phir aik aur sahib ne darwaza khulwaayaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke darwaza khol de aur unhein jannat ki khushkhabri suna de is martaba umr (Raziallahu anhu) they. maine unke liye bhi darwaza khola aur unhein bhi jannat ki khushkhabri suna di. phir aik teesrey sahib ne darwaza khulwaayaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt tek lagaey huey they ab seedhey baith gaey. phir farmaya darwaza khol de aur jannat ki khushkhabri suna de, un aazmaaishon ke sath jis se (duniyaa mein) unhein do-chaar hona padega. main gaya to wahan Usman (Raziallahu anhu) they. unke liye bhi maine darwaza khola aur unhein jannat ki khushkhabri sunai aur wo baat bhi bata di jo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmai thi. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha khair Allah madadgaar hai."
6217,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik janaaza mein Sharik they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein aik chhadi thi usko aap zameen par mar rahe they phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein koi aisa nahi hai jiska jannat ya dozakh ka thikana tay na ho chuka ho. sahaba ne arz kya : phir kyon na ham is par bharosa kar lein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke amal kartey raho kyonke har shakhs jis thikaaney ke liye paida kya gaya hai usko waisii hi taufeeq di jaeygi. jaisa ke Quran sharif ke sura واللیل mein hai) فأما من أعطى واتقى‏ ( ''jisne Allah ki raah mein khairat ki aur Allah Taala se daraa'' aakhir tak.
6218,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (raat mein) bedaar huey aur farmaya '' Subhan-Allah ! Allah ki rehmat ke kitney khazaaney aaj nazil kiye gaey hain aur kis tarah ke fitney bhi utaarey gaey hain. kon hai! jo un hujre waaliyon ko jagaaey.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad paak beeviyon se thi taake wo Namaz padh lein kyonke bahut si duniya mein kapdey pahnney waaliyaan aakhirat mein nangii hongi aur ibne-abii-saur ne bayan kya, unse Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha, kya aap ne paak beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. maine kaha Allaahu-akbar."
6219,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Safiya-bint-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas milney aaein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt masjid mein Ramazan ke aakhiri Ashrey mein aetikaf kiye huey they. isha ke waqt thodi der unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baatein kiin aur wapas lotney ke liye uthein to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi unhein chhod aaney ke liye khadey ho gaey. jab wo masjid ke us darwaza ke paas pahunchein jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ka hujra tha, to idhar se 2 Ansari sahabi guzrey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya aur aagey badh gaey. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke thodi der ke liye thahar jao. ye Safiya-bint-Huyi meri biwi hain. un donon sahaba ne arz kya : sub'haan-Allaah, ya rasoolullaah. un par bada sakht guzraa. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke shaitan insan ke andar khoon ki tarah daudta rehta hai, isliye mujhey khof hua ke kahin wo tumharey dil mein koi shuba na daal de."
6220,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kankari phainkney se mana kya tha aur farmaya tha ke wo na shikar mar sakti hai aur na dushman ko koi nuqsan pahuncha sakti hai, albatta aankh phod sakti hai aur daant tod sakti hai."
6221,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas 2 ashaab chheenkey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik ka jawaab یرحمک اللہ ( Allah tum par raham karey) se diya aur doosrey ka nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uski wjah poochhi gaee to farmaya ke usne الحمدللہ kaha tha (is liye iska jawab diyaa) aur doosrey ne الحمدللہ nahi kaha tha. chheenkney waley ko الحمدللہ zaroor kehna chahiye aur sunney walon ko یرحمک Allaah.
6222,"hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne saat (7) baton ka hukm diya tha aur saat (7) kaamon se rokaa tha, hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bimar ki mizaaj pursi karne, janaaze ke peechhey chalney, chheenkney waley ke jawab dene, dawat karne waley ki dawat qabool karne, salam ka jawab dene, mazloom ki madad karne aur qism kha leney waley ki qism poori karne mein madad dene ka hukm diya tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein saat (7) kaamon se rokaa tha, soney ki anguthi se, ya bayan kya ke soney ke chhalley se, resham aur deebaa aur sundus (deebaa se baareek reshamii kapdaa) pahnney se aur reshamii zeen se."
6223,"aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( farmaya ke) Allah Taala chheenk ko pasand karta hai aur jamaaii ko na-pasand karta hai. isliye jab tum mein se koi shakhs chheenkey aur الحمدللہ kahey to har musalman par jo usey suney , haq hai ke iska jawaab یرحمک اللہ se de. lekin jamaaii shaitan ki taraf se hoti hai isliye jahan tak ho sakey usey rokey kyonke jab wo munh khol kar ha-ha-ha kehta hai to shaitan is par hanstaa hai."
6224,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jab tum mein se koi chheenkey to (alhamdulillah) kahey aur iska bhai ya iska sathi ( rawi ko shuba tha) ( يرحمك الله ( kahey. jab sathi ( يرحمك الله ( kahey to uske jawab mein chheenkney wala ( يهديكم الله ويصلح بالكم ( .''
6225,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maujoodgii mein 2 aadmiyon ne chheenkaa. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein se aik ki chheenk par یرحمک اللہ kaha aur doosrey ki chheenk par nahi kaha, is par doosra shakhs bola ke ya Rasulullah ! aap ne unki chheenk par یرحمک اللہ farmaya, lekin meri chheenk par nahi farmaayaa? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke unhon-ne الحمدللہ kaha tha aur tum ne nahi kaha tha."
6226,Allah Taala chheenk ko pasand karta hai kyonke wo kuchh baar sihat ki alamat hai aur jamaaii ko na-pasand karta hai. isliye jab tum mein se koi shakhs chheenkein to wo الحمدللہ kahey lekin jamaaii lena shaitan ki taraf se hota hai. isliye jab tum mein se kisi ko jamaaii aaey to wo apni quwwat w taqat ke mutabiq usey rokey. isliye ke jab tum mein se koi jamaaii leta hai to shaitan hanstaa hai.
